INSERT INTO `works` (`id`, `title`, `phaseId`, `dateCreated`, `technique`, `dimensions`, `colorPalette`, `emotionalRegister`, `imageUrl`, `imageKey`, `thumbnailUrl`, `journalExcerpt`, `neonReading`, `seriesName`, `isPublished`, `sortOrder`, `createdAt`, `updatedAt`, `featured`, `slug`, `medium`, `year`, `curatorialHook`, `conceptTags`) VALUES (30001,'Big Bang: Breath Aureole',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Subtle cyan undertones','gentle','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB1.jpg','works/bigbang/BB1.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB1.jpg','Feathering, halos, and negative space—saved territory where ink approached but did not consume. Documented throughout series, especially in works emphasizing respiratory quality.','The most delicate specimen in the Big Bang field. Graduated density aureoles and feathering produce a respiratory architecture visible at near-molecular scale: ink approached the white territory but stopped short, leaving halos of negative space that function as the work\'s lung system. A rare cyan undertone breaks the monochrome field like an alchemical trace, color as spirit leaking through the carbon lattice. This is the Breath register isolated and amplified. The painting exhales.','Big Bang',1,2,'2025-12-27 05:54:11','2026-02-12 15:47:08',1,'big-bang-breath-aureole-30001','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','A respiratory calibration of the genesis field where feathering and negative space function as the series’ most delicate evidence of alchemical shift.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30002,'Big Bang: Diagonal Thrust',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray','brutal','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB2.jpg','works/bigbang/BB2.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB2.jpg','The biomechanics are whole-body: shoulder-torso-leg coordination, velocity that requires the full structure, not just wrist. The body becomes the primary instrument.','High-velocity traversal requiring full biomechanical deployment: shoulder-torso-leg coordination at speeds that bypass wrist control entirely. Energy enters one edge and exits another, the edge-bleed confirming the image is an excerpt from a larger force-field, not a self-contained world. Gravity is visible here as compositional co-author, pulling the diagonal toward the lower corner while velocity fights to maintain trajectory. The body that made this was not painting. It was falling forward.','Big Bang',1,3,'2025-12-27 05:54:13','2026-02-12 15:47:08',1,'big-bang-diagonal-thrust-30002','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','Gravity acts as a compositional co-author in this high-velocity traversal, where edge-bleed asserts the logic of an infinite force-field rather than a self-contained world.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30003,'Big Bang: Vertical Descent',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray','brutal','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB3.jpg','works/bigbang/BB3.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB3.jpg','At 100cm x 200cm, these works demand full-body engagement. The paper laid flat on floor or table means the artist moves not as a stationary painter but as a dancer or ritual performer.','Vertical format activates gravity as primary compositional agent. Where Diagonal Thrust records lateral force, this work documents descent: ink falling, pooling, accumulating at the base in sedimentary strata. The body choreography shifts when the paper is oriented vertically; marks trace falling motion rather than sweep. A test specimen for orientation-effect on viscosity behavior. The paper becomes a basin. The ink becomes weather.','Big Bang',1,4,'2025-12-27 05:54:16','2026-02-12 15:47:09',0,'big-bang-vertical-descent-30003','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','A somatic shift in choreography where the marks trace a falling motion, testing the effects of orientation on ink viscosity and the ritual performer’s movement.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30004,'Big Bang: Smoke Field',30009,'2025-05','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Atmospheric smoke','meditative','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB4.jpg','works/bigbang/BB4.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB4.jpg','The Breath—feathering, halos, and negative space representing saved territory where ink approached but did not consume. Essential to preventing the image from collapsing into pure darkness.','Atmospheric-dispersed typology. Cloud-masses and breath-space dominate the field, the Breath register fully activated: graduated density aureoles reading as the work\'s respiratory system made visible. The quietest specimen in the series, holding tension between presence and dissolution. The ink has not struck the paper so much as settled onto it, the way fog settles into a valley. Gravity is present but unhurried. Time is slow here.','Big Bang',1,8,'2025-12-27 05:54:21','2026-02-12 15:47:09',0,'big-bang-smoke-field-30004','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','The series’ most quiet tension between presence and dissolution, where graduated density aureoles activate a fully realized respiratory architecture.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30005,'Big Bang: Diagonal Thrust II',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray','brutal','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB5.jpg','works/bigbang/BB5.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB5.jpg','The series abandons the centralized, mandala-like compositions characterizing Phases 1–3, adopting instead Field logic where energy traverses the picture plane rather than organizing around focal point.','Second expression of the high-velocity diagonal protocol. Where its predecessor emphasized the sweep, this iteration records what happens at the contact zones: ink pooling and accumulating where force meets resistance. The Bone and Flesh registers collaborate, dense blacks providing structural skeleton while mid-tone washes generate turbulence fields. Edge-to-edge movement without center. The series has abandoned the mandala. There is no focal point. There is only transit.','Big Bang',1,5,'2025-12-27 05:54:26','2026-02-12 15:47:10',0,'big-bang-diagonal-thrust-ii-30005','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','An abandonment of centralized, mandala-like focus in favor of field logic, where dense blacks and mid-tone washes collaborate to document ink pooling at contact zones.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30006,'Big Bang: Geological Core',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Turbulent mid-tones','brutal','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB6.jpg','works/bigbang/BB6.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB6.jpg','The ink demonstrates distinctive viscosity regime. Register 2: The Flesh—mid-tone washes and granulation, produced through geological or biological micro-textures, result of ink sediment settling into paper fiber topography.','Dense-geological at center with atmospheric halo at periphery. The Flesh register dominates: mid-tone washes producing geological micro-textures as ink sediment settles into the paper fiber topography. This is compression made visible, viscosity creating internal complexity and depth not through the artist\'s gesture but through gravity\'s patient collaboration with material. What you see is not what was painted. It is what accumulated.','Big Bang',1,6,'2025-12-27 05:54:30','2026-02-12 15:47:10',0,'big-bang-geological-core-30006','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','The Flesh register dominates through a distinctive viscosity regime, where ink sediment settles into the paper fiber topography to create a geological micro-texture.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30007,'Big Bang: Breath & Bone',30009,'2025-04','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray','meditative','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB7.jpg','works/bigbang/BB7.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB7.jpg','Register 1: The Bone—highest density blacks, sits on paper fiber rather than soaking through, creates foreground depth with almost three-dimensional presence, functions as structural skeleton.','Hybrid-transitional specimen demonstrating the full duality of the viscosity system. The Bone provides structural skeleton at center: highest-density blacks sitting on top of the paper fiber with near three-dimensional presence. The Breath creates halos and feathering at the edges, saving territory where ink approached but did not consume. The container is no longer drawn. It is enacted through ink\'s inherent behavior encountering paper\'s inherent resistance. Physics decided where the boundary would fall.','Big Bang',1,7,'2025-12-27 05:54:34','2026-02-12 15:47:10',0,'big-bang-breath-bone-30007','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','A hybrid-transitional work demonstrating the duality of the viscosity system, where the container is no longer drawn but enacted through the ink’s inherent behavior.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30008,'Big Bang: Geological Core II',30009,'2025-05','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Dense turbulent center','brutal','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB8.jpg','works/bigbang/BB8.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB8.jpg','The ink pools, settles, responds to earth pull. Paper becomes a basin catching what falls. This is not possible with vertical easel work.','Maximum compression at center with explosive periphery. Where Geological Core documented formation, this work documents pressure: strata compressed into near-singularity, the Flesh register generating turbulence, density, and internal heat. Ink as tectonic force. The pools settled, responded to earth-pull, and the paper became a basin catching what falls. This is not possible with vertical easel work. The floor is the collaborator.','Big Bang',1,9,'2025-12-27 05:54:38','2026-02-12 15:47:11',0,'big-bang-geological-core-ii-30008','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','Maximum compression at the center transforms the paper into a basin, catching the fallout of ink as a tectonic force responding to the earth’s pull.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30009,'Big Bang: Cloud Mass',30009,'2025-05','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Atmospheric wash','meditative','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB9.jpg','works/bigbang/BB9.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB9.jpg','These works function as temples dedicated to the act of creation rather than documents of it. Temple is not photograph of worship but site where worship occurred and can occur again.','Atmospheric-dispersed, cousin to Smoke Field. Cloud-masses dominate, the work hovering in the unstable zone between representation (it looks like clouds) and abstraction (it is ink behavior). Field logic at its most elemental: pure atmosphere, pure breath, minimal structure. These works function as temples dedicated to the act of creation rather than documents of it. Temple is not photograph of worship but site where worship occurred and can occur again.','Big Bang',1,10,'2025-12-27 05:54:42','2026-02-12 15:47:11',0,'big-bang-cloud-mass-30009','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','Pure atmospheric breath that hovers between representational weather systems and elemental field logic, marking the series’ most minimal structural state.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30010,'Big Bang: Shadow Self',30009,'2025-05','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Warm ochre undertones','mysterious','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB10.jpg','works/bigbang/BB10.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/bigbang/BB10.jpg','Most bounded, creature-like form in series. If Shadow were to have shape, it might look like this—entity floating against void, both part of self and separate from it.','The outlier. Bounded-figural rather than field-based, this work reads as organism against void: a confrontation with the Shadow Self in Jungian terms. Warm ochre undertones, absent from the cooler atmospheric grays of the other specimens, mark this as the series\' reckoning with darkness not as absence but as presence. The only work that registers as figure rather than force. Something is in there. It is looking back.','Big Bang',1,11,'2025-12-27 05:54:46','2026-02-12 15:47:12',0,'big-bang-shadow-self-30010','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','A bounded-figural outlier that confronts the Jungian shadow, utilizing warm ochre undertones to mark darkness as a presence rather than an absence.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30011,'Thr3e (standing Bruise)',30009,'2025-08-26','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 100cm','Black, Gray, Tar-like matte monolith mass with central bruise-light wound','gravitas','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/thr3e/THR3E.jpg','works/thr3e/THR3E.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/thr3e/THR3E.jpg','This painting is the Anchor of the 2025 series. While the rectangular works (100cm × 200cm) are the Explorations, this square work is the Definition. It proves that the New Era is not just about size or movement, but about density and presence.','The square format is a trap. Where the rectangular Big Bang works allow energy to bleed outward along the longer axis, this format reflects force back into the interior, building internal pressure until the image becomes a sealed vessel. Thr3e compresses eruptive field-logic into crucible-logic. The bruise-light at center is not transcendent: it is persistent, the survival of consciousness within overwhelming shadow. This is the moment the practice shifts from meteorology (storms that pass) to geology (bedrock that persists). The Anchor specimen. The Definition.','Thr3e',1,12,'2025-12-27 06:06:01','2026-02-23 19:19:17',1,'thr3e-standing-bruise-30011','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','The definitive specimen of the New Era, compressing the eruptive Big Bang field into a square pressure vessel to document the survival of consciousness under pressure.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30012,'Covenant I: Storm-body',30009,'2025-09-21','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Horizontal turbulence','solemn aftermath','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic2.jpg','works/covenant/COVTryptic2.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic2.jpg','Panel I: Collapse and turbulence. The monolithic presence has shattered into horizontal chaos. This is the storm-body that must be organized.','Panel I. The first stage of the law: acknowledging chaos. Horizontal flows without coherence, lower masses weighted and collapsed. The monolithic presence has shattered into turbulence. This is the shadow before it becomes architecture, the raw material of disorder that the subsequent panels will organize. Not failure. Inventory.','Covenant',1,13,'2025-12-27 06:22:52','2026-02-24 08:15:02',1,'covenant-i-storm-body-30012','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','The first stage of the law: a visual acknowledgment of horizontal chaos and collapsed masses before they are organized into ritual architecture.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30013,'Covenant II: Vessel-body',30009,'2025-09-21','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Rib-like voids','solemn aftermath','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic3.jpg','works/covenant/COVTryptic3.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic3.jpg','Panel II: Structure. Organizes around a vertical axis with rib-like void chambers. Pressure energy holds what the storm scattered.','Panel II. The second stage: containment. A vertical axis appears where Storm-body had none, organizing the chaos into load-bearing structure with rib-like void chambers. Pressure energy holds what the storm scattered. This is the crucible at work, weight becoming architecture, disorder becoming vessel. The transition from entropy to order is not gradual. It is structural. Something clicked into place.','Covenant',1,14,'2025-12-27 06:22:57','2026-02-25 01:08:40',1,'covenant-ii-vessel-body-30013','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','The appearance of a vertical axis organizes chaos into a load-bearing structure, literalizing the transition from weight to architectural containment.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30014,'Covenant III: Threshold-body',30009,'2025-09-21','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','100cm x 200cm','Black, Gray, Opening luminosity','solemn aftermath','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic1.jpg','works/covenant/COVTryptic1.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/covenant/COVTryptic1.jpg','Panel III: Emergence. Upward trajectories and a clear threshold. Release energy lifts and opens the void as a luminous portal.','Panel III. The third stage: release. Marks thin and lift, opening a coherent void. Upward trajectories and a clear threshold. This is negative light: luminosity created through emptiness organized into a gateway. The Covenant is sealed here. Chaos became vessel became door.','Covenant',1,15,'2025-12-27 06:23:02','2026-02-25 01:09:07',0,'covenant-iii-threshold-body-30014','Sumi ink on Chinese mulberry paper','2025','Luminosity is created through emptiness, sealing the covenant by opening the negative space into a coherent portal of release.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30015,'Ode to Osiris',30004,'2020-08','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Copper, Dense knot','reverent resignation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/1_ode_to_osiris_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/equinox/1_ode_to_osiris_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/1_ode_to_osiris_peteryuill(1).jpg','Osiris: the dying-and-resurrecting god. Sacrifice, judgment, external law. This dense symmetrical knot represents the old aeon—the sacrificial and authoritarian structure that must be transcended. Copper grounds it in the earthly and material.','Acknowledgment of the old order. Osiris: the dying-and-resurrecting god, sacrifice, judgment, external law. This dense symmetrical knot represents the sacrificial and authoritarian structure of the old aeon. Copper grounds it in the earthly and material. The knot is closed, complete, memorial. A specimen of what must be left behind, documented before burning.','Equinox of the Gods',1,1,'2025-12-27 06:45:40','2026-02-12 15:47:14',0,'ode-to-osiris-30015','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2020','A memoriam of the old aeon\'s sacrificial and authoritarian structure, grounded in earthly copper to represent the external law that must be transcended.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30016,'Ode to Isis',30004,'2020-08','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Gold, Dense knot','reverent contained grief','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/2_ode_to_isis_peteryuill(2).jpg','works/equinox/2_ode_to_isis_peteryuill(2).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/2_ode_to_isis_peteryuill(2).jpg','Isis: ancient mother goddess. Magic, wisdom, fertility. The pre-historical matriarchal aeon—instinct, nature, the body. This dense symmetrical knot honors the origin, the feminine-instinctual foundation. Gold illuminates the celestial and sacred.','Acknowledgment of origin. Isis: ancient mother goddess, magic, wisdom, fertility. The pre-historical matriarchal aeon: instinct, nature, the body. This dense symmetrical knot honors the ancestral ground, the feminine-instinctual foundation. Gold illuminates the celestial and sacred. The knot is contained, reverent. Departure requires knowing where you depart from.','Equinox of the Gods',1,2,'2025-12-27 06:45:42','2026-02-12 15:47:14',0,'ode-to-isis-30016','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2020','An acknowledgment of the instinctual foundation, where a contained gold knot honors the ancient feminine origin from which all transformation departs.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30017,'Ode to Hadit',30004,'2020-08','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Open vortex with central void','intense coiled potential','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/3_ode_to_hadit_peteryuill(2).jpg','works/equinox/3_ode_to_hadit_peteryuill(2).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/3_ode_to_hadit_peteryuill(2).jpg','Hadit: the infinitely small point of pure will. The concentrated self, the inner flame. This open vortex spirals toward a central white void—inward-pulling energy, the distillation of the new self. The essential point from which all will emanates.','Distillation to essential will. Hadit: the infinitely small point of pure intention. This open vortex spirals inward toward a central white void. Not expansion but concentration. The new aeon\'s core is not a god to worship but a point to become. Everything the Equinox series has been building toward contracts here into a singularity. The knowing distilled to a single point.','Equinox of the Gods',1,3,'2025-12-27 06:45:44','2026-02-12 15:47:15',0,'ode-to-hadit-30017','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2020','A distillation of the individuated will, where an inward-pulling vortex spirals toward a central white void as the inner flame of the new aeon.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30018,'Ode to Hoor-pa-kraat',30004,'2020-08','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Copper, Extremely dense knot','silent restrained power','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/6_ode_to_hoor_pa_kraat_peteryuill(2).jpg','works/equinox/6_ode_to_hoor_pa_kraat_peteryuill(2).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/6_ode_to_hoor_pa_kraat_peteryuill(2).jpg','Hoor-pa-kraat (Harpocrates): the silent child-god. Self-possession, patience, inner knowing. This extremely dense knot holds immense pressure in perfect containment. Silent power, compressed energy, disciplined restraint—the moment before action.','Silent containment of knowing. Hoor-pa-kraat: the silent child-god, self-possession, patience, inner knowing. This extremely dense knot holds immense pressure in perfect equilibrium. Maximum force with zero release. The moment before action. The coiled spring. The held breath. In the Equinox sequence, this is the specimen of disciplined restraint: power not wielded but held.','Equinox of the Gods',1,4,'2025-12-27 06:45:50','2026-02-12 15:47:15',0,'ode-to-hoor-pa-kraat-30018','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2020','A study in disciplined restraint, where maximum pressure is held in perfect containment to represent self-knowledge as a silent, patient power.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30019,'Ode to Therion',30004,'2020-08','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','100cm x 100cm','Black, Gold, Copper, Fractured vortex','ecstatic volatile rupture','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/7_ode_to_therion_peteryuill.jpg','works/equinox/7_ode_to_therion_peteryuill.jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/equinox/7_ode_to_therion_peteryuill.jpg','Therion: The Beast. Crowley\'s magickal name—the unleashed will, full self-actualization, aeonic rupture. This large fractured vortex explodes outward, containment shattered. Dual gold and copper fuse celestial and terrestrial into volatile unity. This is the climax: all containment breaks, the new self becomes undeniable.','Explosive release and full activation. Therion: the Beast, the unleashed will, aeonic rupture. The largest work in the series detonates where Hoor-pa-kraat held. The fractured vortex explodes outward, containment shattered. Dual gold and copper fuse celestial and terrestrial into volatile unity. This is not peace. This is dangerous becoming. The transformation is irreversible. Every seal broken.','Equinox of the Gods',1,5,'2025-12-27 06:45:53','2026-02-12 15:47:16',0,'ode-to-therion-30019','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2020','The climax of aeonic rupture, where all containment shatters and dual metals fuse into a volatile unity of irreversible self-actualization.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30020,'The Limitless Path of the Intuitive Mind I',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Continuous flow','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','A horizontal chain of linked torus forms against a gold circular plane. The voids create an endless corridor—the path forward is infinite, and the intuitive mind navigates through knowing, not logic.','A horizontal chain of linked torus forms against a gold circular plane. The voids create an endless corridor: the path extends infinitely, navigated by knowing rather than logic. Alignment as ongoing practice, not arrival. The gold marks the path as sacred. No destination. Just sustained motion through mystery.','Alignment',1,1,'2025-12-27 06:54:12','2026-02-12 15:47:16',0,'the-limitless-path-of-the-intuitive-mind-i-30020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','Gold illuminates a continuous horizontal flow of linked torus forms, suggesting consciousness navigating through mystery without the demand for resolution.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30021,'The Limitless Path of the Intuitive Mind Ii',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Copper, Continuous flow','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_limitless_path_of_the_intuitive_mind_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','Similar horizontal chain, but copper replaces gold. The path is now earthbound, embodied, rooted. Where gold elevated, copper grounds. Both paths are valid—one celestial, one terrestrial.','Grounded twin of the elevated path. Copper replaces gold, pulling the journey from the celestial to the terrestrial. Where gold elevated, copper anchors. The work insists that spiritual practice is not escape from the physical. It is movement through both registers simultaneously. The same path, different frequency.','Alignment',1,2,'2025-12-27 06:54:14','2026-02-12 15:47:17',0,'the-limitless-path-of-the-intuitive-mind-ii-30021','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','The grounded twin of the celestial journey, using copper to anchor spiritual practice within the bodily and material register.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30022,'The Infinite Plane I',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Symmetrical expansion','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','Four interconnected torus forms on a gold backdrop. The plane extends horizontally without hierarchy or destination—each node equal in the infinite network.','Four interconnected torus forms on a gold backdrop. No single form dominates. Each is an equal node in a distributed network. Non-hierarchical cosmology: consciousness spread across the field, not concentrated at a center. The plane extends without destination or hierarchy. Gold equalizes.','Alignment',1,3,'2025-12-27 06:54:16','2026-02-12 15:47:17',0,'the-infinite-plane-i-30022','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A non-hierarchical cosmology where gold equalizes a network of interconnected nodes, distributing consciousness across an infinite field.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30023,'The Infinite Plane Ii',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Copper, Symmetrical expansion','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/the_infinite_plane_2_peteryuill(1).jpg','Four interconnected torus forms on a copper backdrop. Simpler than the Limitless Path series—more symmetrical, more stable. The plane extends horizontally without hierarchy or destination.','Copper variant of the distributed network. More symmetrical, more stable than the Limitless Path works. The plane extends without hierarchy or destination. Copper stabilizes where gold illuminates. The same cosmological principle, grounded in different frequency.','Alignment',1,4,'2025-12-27 06:54:17','2026-02-12 15:47:18',0,'the-infinite-plane-ii-30023','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','Copper stabilizes the plane as the ground of being, insisting on a symmetrical and stable distribution of awareness without destination.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30024,'Dreamcatcher',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Gold, Quatrefoil web','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/dreamcatcher_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/dreamcatcher_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/dreamcatcher_peteryuill(1).jpg','A quatrefoil knot with gold arcs forming a woven web. The central void becomes a portal or trap. Dreamcatcher bridges Indigenous North American symbolism with Norse and Hermetic geometry—catching what passes between worlds.','A quatrefoil knot with gold arcs forming a woven web. The central void operates as portal or filter: noise is held, meaning passes through. Gold arcs define the protective structure. The void at center is not empty. It is the site where the threshold operates. A sorting mechanism for what crosses between worlds.','Alignment',1,5,'2025-12-27 06:54:19','2026-02-12 15:47:18',0,'dreamcatcher-30024','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A protective geometry that filters existential noise, bridging indigenous symbolism with Hermetic geometry to catch what passes between worlds.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30025,'Aurorae Aureae',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Copper, Radial spiral','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/aurorae_aureae_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/aurorae_aureae_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/aurorae_aureae_peteryuill(1).jpg','Radial torus forms spiraling outward from a copper central disk. Golden auroras—light emerging from grounded center. The composition breathes outward, aurora-like, from a bodily core.','Radial torus forms spiraling outward from a copper central disk. Golden aurorae: light emerging from grounded center. The composition breathes outward, aurora-like, from a bodily core. The work insists that transcendence begins in the body, not above it. Copper disk is the origin. Gold spirals are the emission.','Alignment',1,6,'2025-12-27 06:54:21','2026-02-12 15:47:19',0,'aurorae-aureae-30025','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','Transcendence begins in the bodily core, visualized through a copper disk that anchors a radial spiral of golden lights emerging from the earth.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30026,'Inside the Vortex',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Dense radial mandala','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/inside_the_vortex_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/inside_the_vortex_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/inside_the_vortex_peteryuill(1).jpg','The most intricate work in the series. A dense radial mandala with torus forms spiraling inward toward a gold central disk and black void. The viewer is pulled into the center—not escape, but immersion.','The most intricate specimen in the Alignment series. A dense radial mandala with torus forms spiraling inward toward a gold central disk and black void. The viewer is pulled toward the center: not escape but total absorption. Meditation rendered as geometry. The slow inward spiral that replaces thought with presence. The eye cannot rest. It must follow the geometry in.','Alignment',1,7,'2025-12-27 06:54:24','2026-02-12 15:47:19',0,'inside-the-vortex-30026','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','Meditation made visible through an intricate inward spiral that replaces thought with presence, pulling the viewer into total absorption.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30027,'Freyja',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Copper, Four-directional cross','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/freyja_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/freyja_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/freyja_peteryuill(1).jpg','Named for the Norse goddess of love, fertility, and war. A vertical cross configuration with copper accent arcs—grounded, embodied, fierce feminine power radiating in four directions.','Named for the Norse goddess of love, fertility, and war. Vertical cross configuration with copper accent arcs: grounded, embodied, fierce feminine power radiating in four directions from a rooted center. Power as embodied presence, not elevation. Copper marks terrestrial sovereignty.','Alignment',1,8,'2025-12-27 06:54:26','2026-02-12 15:47:19',0,'freyja-30027','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A vertical cross configuration in copper that radiates grounded feminine power as an embodied presence rather than an elevated ideal.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30028,'Freyr',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Gold, Four-directional cross','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/freyr_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/freyr_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/freyr_peteryuill(1).jpg','Named for the Norse god of sunshine, prosperity, and fair weather. A vertical cross configuration with gold accent arcs—solar, elevated, radiating benevolent masculine energy in four directions.','Named for the Norse god of sunshine, prosperity, and fair weather. Gold replaces copper. Celestial masculine axis where Freyja was terrestrial feminine. Paired, the two works form a binary: earth/sky, copper/gold, embodied/elevated. Together they complete the cosmological circuit.','Alignment',1,9,'2025-12-27 06:54:29','2026-02-12 15:47:20',0,'freyr-30028','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','The celestial masculine axis, utilizing gold solar radiance to complete the cosmology when paired with its terrestrial counterpart.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30029,'As Above, So Below I',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Quatrefoil symmetry','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/as_above_so_below_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/as_above_so_below_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/as_above_so_below_1_peteryuill(1).jpg','A quatrefoil knot with gold arcs. The title invokes the Hermetic axiom—macrocosm and microcosm mirror each other. Four-fold symmetry suggests cosmic correspondence: the same laws govern atoms and galaxies.','A quatrefoil knot with gold arcs. The title invokes the Hermetic axiom directly: macrocosm and microcosm mirror each other. Four-fold symmetry proposes cosmic correspondence. The work insists sacred geometry is not symbolic. It is literal correspondence between scales of reality. The same laws govern atoms and galaxies.','Alignment',1,10,'2025-12-27 06:54:31','2026-02-12 15:47:20',0,'as-above-so-below-i-30029','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A literal geometric correspondence between scales of reality, invoking the Hermetic axiom through four-fold cosmic symmetry.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30030,'Polaris',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Vertical lemniscate','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/polaris_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/polaris_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/polaris_peteryuill(1).jpg','A vertical figure-eight (infinity symbol) with gold accent shapes threading through the loops. Named for the North Star—fixed point, orientation, navigation through chaos. Two voids suggest vertical axis: as above, so below.','A vertical lemniscate with gold accent shapes threading through the loops. Named for the North Star: the fixed point around which everything else rotates. Two voids in vertical alignment hold heaven and earth, spirit and body in continuous circulation. Gold threads through both registers. Alignment as anchor, not destination.','Alignment',1,11,'2025-12-27 06:54:33','2026-02-12 15:47:21',0,'polaris-30030','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','The lemniscate as an orienting axis, aligning spirit and body around a fixed point of navigation within the vertical alignment of the North Star.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30031,'Golden Dawn',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Radial emergence','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/golden_dawn_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/golden_dawn_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/golden_dawn_peteryuill(1).jpg','Radial torus forms emerging from central void. The title references both the natural phenomenon and the Hermetic Order—light breaking through darkness, initiation into mystery.','Radial torus forms emerging from central void. The title references both natural phenomenon and Hermetic Order: light breaking through darkness, initiation into mystery. Gold marks the emergence. The work captures the liminal instant when darkness gives way. Not sudden, but gradual, radial, inevitable. Initiation as natural process.','Alignment',1,12,'2025-12-27 06:54:34','2026-02-12 15:47:21',0,'golden-dawn-30031','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A radial initiation into mystery, capturing the gradual threshold moment where light inevitably emerges from the central void.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30032,'Vibrational Alignment',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Resonant geometry','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/vibrational_alignment_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/vibrational_alignment_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/vibrational_alignment_peteryuill(1).jpg','Torus forms arranged in resonant configuration. The title suggests frequency, harmony, attunement—the work as tuning fork for consciousness.','Torus forms in resonant configuration. The geometry creates visual resonance: forms that seem to hum at a frequency beyond hearing. Gold amplifies the vibration. This is the exhibition\'s namesake made manifest. Alignment not as spatial position but as vibrational frequency. A tuning fork for consciousness.','Alignment',1,13,'2025-12-27 06:54:36','2026-02-12 15:47:22',0,'vibrational-alignment-30032','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','Geometry as a tuning fork for consciousness, where resonant forms hum at a frequency amplified by the presence of gold.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(30033,'A Walking Bundle of Frequencies',30003,'2019-2020','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Gold, Dynamic flow','calm meditative grounded','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/a_walking_bundle_of_frequencies_peteryuill(1).jpg','works/alignment/a_walking_bundle_of_frequencies_peteryuill(1).jpg','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/alignment/a_walking_bundle_of_frequencies_peteryuill(1).jpg','Torus forms in dynamic arrangement suggesting movement, embodiment, the human as vibrational entity. We are not solid—we are frequencies walking.','Torus forms in dynamic arrangement suggesting movement and embodiment. The title captures the thesis: we are not fixed, not solid, not singular. Walking bundles of frequencies, vibrations temporarily cohered into form. Gold marks the coherence. The voids mark the spaces between notes. The human as waveform.','Alignment',1,14,'2025-12-27 06:54:38','2026-02-12 15:47:22',0,'a-walking-bundle-of-frequencies-30033','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2019','A thesis on the human as a non-solid entity, where gold marks the temporary coherence of vibrations and voids mark the spaces between notes.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60001,'Echoes',30005,'2022','Acrylic paint on linen','200cm x 200cm','Black, Gold, Cosmic saturation','cosmic monumental','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Echoes(2x2m).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Echoes(2x2m).jpg','The monumental centerpiece of the phase. 2x2 meters. Four-directional symmetry mapping a cosmic broadcast. This is the echo chamber where the signal is received.','The monumental centerpiece. Two meters square. Acrylic on linen. Four-directional symmetry mapping a cosmic broadcast. At this scale the geometry demands full-body engagement: you cannot take it in from a single position. The artist as antenna, capturing a cosmic signal and amplifying it through material. The echo chamber where transmission is received and made visible.','Echoes',1,1,'2025-12-27 07:41:24','2026-02-12 15:47:22',0,'echoes-60001','Acrylic paint on linen','2022','The altarpiece of conduit consciousness, where massive scale requires the artist to act as an antenna capturing and amplifying a cosmic broadcast.',NULL),(60002,'Valis',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','sci-fi gnosis','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Valis.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Valis.jpg','Named for Philip K. Dick\'s Vast Active Living Intelligence System. A vertical stack of spheres acting as a transmission beam. Gnostic sci-fi meets sacred geometry.','Named for Philip K. Dick\'s Vast Active Living Intelligence System. A vertical stack of spheres functioning as transmission beam. Gnostic sci-fi meets sacred geometry. The title confirms the intent: information beamed from a vast intelligence into the human conduit. The geometry is a receiver for pink light data.','Echoes',1,2,'2025-12-27 07:41:26','2026-02-12 15:47:23',0,'valis-60002','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A gnostic transmission beam that confirms the intent of information being beamed from a vast intelligence into the geometric receiver.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60003,'Electric Dreams',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','sci-fi gnosis','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Electricdream.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Electricdream.jpg','Reference to Philip K. Dick. Vertical spheres with distinct \'Saturn ring\' distortions. The boundary between artificial and organic intelligence blurs in the moiré field.','Philip K. Dick reference. Vertical spheres with distinct Saturn-ring distortions. The boundary between artificial and organic intelligence blurs in the moiré interference field. Simulation theory rendered in ink. The moiré patterns create digital-analog interference, visualizing the glitch in consensus reality.','Echoes',1,3,'2025-12-27 07:41:27','2026-02-12 15:47:23',0,'electric-dreams-60003','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','Simulation theory rendered in ink, where moiré fields and Saturn ring distortions visualize the digital-analog interference of a holographic universe.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60004,'A Momentary Lapse of Reason',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','surrendered','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/AMomentarilyLapseofReason.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/AMomentarilyLapseofReason.jpg','Pink Floyd reference. A vertical alignment where logic suspends. This marks the shift to conduit consciousness—reason lapses, and something else takes over.','Pink Floyd reference. A vertical alignment where logic suspends. This marks the shift to conduit consciousness: reason lapses, and something else takes over. The title celebrates the breakdown, the moment the ego steps aside and the signal comes through unfiltered. Geometry not as logic but as trance state.','Echoes',1,4,'2025-12-27 07:41:28','2026-02-12 15:47:24',0,'a-momentary-lapse-of-reason-60004','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','The suspension of logic and the ego\'s withdrawal, marking the definitive shift where the rational mind collapses to allow the signal through.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60005,'Labyrinth of Coral Caves (1)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','deep interiority','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/LabyrinthofCoralCaves.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/LabyrinthofCoralCaves.jpg','Complex, multi-sphere arrangement creating a visual labyrinth. Dense moiré patterns pull the eye into deep interiority. A map of the subconscious structures.','Complex multi-sphere arrangement creating visual labyrinth. Dense moiré patterns pull the eye into deep interiority. A map of subconscious structures. The labyrinth is not for getting lost but for finding the center. Visual density creates a cave effect: psychic depth rendered as surface tension.','Echoes',1,5,'2025-12-27 07:41:30','2026-02-12 15:47:24',0,'labyrinth-of-coral-caves-1-60005','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A map of subconscious structures that utilizes psychic depth and surface tension to find the center within the visual labyrinth.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60006,'Gravity Well',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','35cm x 70cm','Black, Moiré distortion','heavy pull','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Gravitywell.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Gravitywell.jpg','A massive single sphere with intense optical pull. Physics as spiritual metaphor: gravity bends light and time. The viewer is pulled into the event horizon.','A massive single sphere with intense optical pull. Physics as spiritual metaphor: gravity bends light and time. This is not a picture of a planet. It is a diagram of attraction. The visual weight is palpable. The eye falls into it the way matter falls into a gravity well. Event horizon in ink.','Echoes',1,6,'2025-12-27 07:41:38','2026-02-12 15:47:25',0,'gravity-well-60006','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','Physics as a spiritual metaphor, where a massive single sphere demonstrates the event horizon as a palpable diagram of attraction.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60007,'Amnesia',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','erased','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Amnesia.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Amnesia.jpg','Vertical structure, stripped back. Amnesia is the precondition for channeling—you must forget who you are to become the conduit.','Vertical structure, stripped back. Amnesia is the precondition for channeling: you must forget who you are to become the conduit. The clearing of the buffer. The vessel must be empty to receive. This work feels lighter, blanker than the dense transmissions. Erasure as preparation.','Echoes',1,7,'2025-12-27 07:41:40','2026-02-12 15:47:25',0,'amnesia-60007','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','The precondition for channeling, where the clearing of the mental buffer and the emptying of the vessel allow for the reception of the signal','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60008,'Persistence of Time (1)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','21cm x 30cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/17.1.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/17.1.jpg','Numbered work from the Echoes series. A specific frequency or coordinate in the cosmic map. Vertical alignment.','Logged coordinate. Small-scale vertical alignment. Part of the systematic mapping of the cosmic signal. Raw transmission fragment, un-titled, just indexed. A frequency recorded.','Echoes',1,8,'2025-12-27 07:41:41','2026-02-12 15:47:26',0,'persistence-of-time-1-60008','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','Raw coordinate data from the transmission, logged as a specific frequency within the cosmic mapping sequence.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60009,'Section 9',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/9.1.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/9.1.jpg','Numbered work. Dense moiré patterns creating a chaotic interference field. The signal is noisy here.','Dense moiré patterns generating chaotic interference field. The signal is noisy here: high-frequency interference overwhelming the carrier wave. The channel is open but the data saturates the receiving capacity. Static as content.','Echoes',1,9,'2025-12-27 07:41:43','2026-02-12 15:47:26',0,'section-9-60009','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A chaotic interference field where the density of the moiré suggests the signal is open but the data is overwhelming.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60010,'Labyrinth of Coral Caves (2)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/13(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/13(1).jpg','Numbered work. Vertical alignment. Simpler frequency.','Simpler frequency than its predecessor. Vertical alignment. The carrier wave has stabilized. A clear transmission through the coral architecture.','Echoes',1,10,'2025-12-27 07:41:44','2026-02-12 15:47:26',0,'labyrinth-of-coral-caves-2-60010','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A stable carrier wave that manifests as clear vertical transmission, signifying a moment of signal clarity.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60011,'Genesis',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','originary','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Genesis.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Genesis.jpg','The beginning. A ring of spheres surrounding a central dense core. The moment of cosmic creation rendered in ink.','Origin point. A ring of spheres surrounding a central dense core. Cosmogony in ink: the birth of a universe. The ring formation is protective, incubating the dense center. The moment before the first expansion.','Echoes',1,11,'2025-12-27 07:41:45','2026-02-12 15:47:27',0,'genesis-60011','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','Cosmogony rendered in ink, where a ring of spheres incubates a dense central core at the moment of cosmic creation.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60012,'Split Second',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, Moiré interference','instantaneous','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Spitsecond.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/Spitsecond.jpg','Two massive spheres in vertical alignment, connected at a single point. The moment of contact. Time compressed.','Two massive spheres in vertical alignment connected at a single tangent point. The infinitesimal moment of contact between two cosmic bodies. Time compressed to a point of contact. The moiré creates temporal shimmer, the image oscillating between before-contact and after-contact simultaneously.','Echoes',1,12,'2025-12-27 07:41:47','2026-02-12 15:47:27',0,'split-second-60012','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','The temporal compression of an infinitesimal moment of contact between two massive cosmic bodies.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60013,'Major Motoko',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, Moiré interference','cybernetic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/MajorMotoko.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/MajorMotoko.jpg','Named for the Ghost in the Shell protagonist. A vertical stack with satellite spheres. The cyborg consciousness—human and machine merged.','Named for the Ghost in the Shell protagonist. Vertical stack with satellite spheres. The cyborg consciousness: human and machine merged. Kusanagi questioning her own humanity. The geometry suggests a body that is both organic and constructed. The ghost is in the geometry.','Echoes',1,13,'2025-12-27 07:41:48','2026-02-12 15:47:28',0,'major-motoko-60013','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A cybernetic geometry that invokes the merger of organic and constructed consciousness, questioning the boundaries of the ghost in the shell.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60014,'Orbital Refraction',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','100cm x 70cm','Black, Moiré interference','expansive','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/OrbitalRefraction.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/OrbitalRefraction.jpg','Complex multi-sphere arrangement with horizontal expansion. Light bending around massive objects. The physics of perception.','Complex multi-sphere arrangement with horizontal expansion. Gravitational lensing rendered in ink: what we see is not what is, but what gravity allows us to see. Light bending around massive objects. The physics of perception as the physics of deception.','Echoes',1,14,'2025-12-27 07:41:50','2026-02-12 15:47:28',0,'orbital-refraction-60014','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','The physics of perception visualized through gravitational lensing, showing how space-time warps around mass to dictate what the eye is allowed to see.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60015,'A Delicate Sound of Thunder',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','100cm x 70cm','Black, Moiré interference','atmospheric','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/DelicateSoundofThunder.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/DelicateSoundofThunder.jpg','Pink Floyd reference. Horizontal composition with central mass and radiating satellite spheres. The sound of distant cosmic events.','Pink Floyd reference. Horizontal composition with central mass and radiating satellites. Something massive happening far away, felt rather than heard. The horizontal format creates a landscape of cosmic weather. Distant detonation. The shockwave hasn\'t arrived yet.','Echoes',1,15,'2025-12-27 07:41:51','2026-02-12 15:47:29',0,'a-delicate-sound-of-thunder-60015','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A landscape of cosmic weather where distant, massive events are felt through the resonance of radiating satellite spheres.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60016,'Persistence of Time (2)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','21cm x 30cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/18.1(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/18.1(1).jpg','Numbered work. Vertical stack with satellite spheres. Part of the coordinate series.','Another frequency logged. Vertical stack with satellite spheres. The numbered series continues systematic mapping of the cosmic signal. Data point in an ongoing survey.','Echoes',1,16,'2025-12-27 07:41:53','2026-02-12 15:47:29',0,'persistence-of-time-2-60016','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A systematic logging of another frequency, continuing the coordinate series through a vertical stack of satellite spheres.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60017,'Persistence of Time (3)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','21cm x 30cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/19.1.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/19.1.jpg','Numbered work. Vertical alignment with three spheres. Simple, clear transmission.','Three spheres in vertical alignment. Simple, clear transmission. The signal is coming through clean. Stable frequency. Minimal interference.','Echoes',1,17,'2025-12-27 07:41:57','2026-02-12 15:47:30',0,'persistence-of-time-3-60017','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A clear channel transmission where the simplicity of the vertical alignment suggests a stable and clean frequency.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(60018,'Persistence of Time (4)',30005,'2022','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 21cm','Black, Moiré interference','cryptic','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/20.1.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/echoes/20.1.jpg','Numbered work. Complex vertical arrangement with multiple satellite spheres.','Complex vertical arrangement with multiple satellites. Multiple signals overlapping. Dense but structured data. The survey encounters a cluster.','Echoes',1,18,'2025-12-27 07:41:59','2026-02-12 15:47:30',0,'persistence-of-time-4-60018','Ink on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2022','A complex vertical arrangement where multiple overlapping signals create a dense but structured data set.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90001,'Cross Mandala with Gold Center',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','celestial symmetry','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0012(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0012(1).jpg','Four-directional symmetry. Central gold circle surrounded by ink spheres and satellite forms radiating outward. Saturn rings visible in moiré patterns. This is the cosmos as mandala—order and chaos held in equilibrium.','Four-directional symmetry. Central gold circle surrounded by ink spheres radiating outward. Saturn rings visible in moiré patterns. The cosmos rendered as mandala: order and chaos held in equilibrium. The gold center is the sun, the still point. Ink spheres are orbital bodies caught in the gravitational field.','Celestial Secrets',1,1,'2025-12-27 07:59:24','2026-02-12 15:47:30',0,'cross-mandala-with-gold-center-90001','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','The sun as a still point in a mandala of cardinal completeness, holding planetary ink spheres in equilibrium.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90002,'Horizontal Orbital Mural (study)',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','600cm x 150cm','Black, Gold, White','architectural presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/20230628_223310~2.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/20230628_223310~2.jpg','Installation shot from West Eden Gallery. Large horizontal orbital composition. Circular forms overlap, creating moiré interference fields. Gold leaf accents at key gravitational points. The work occupies the wall like a cosmic event horizon.','Architectural-scale specimen, 600cm wide. Circular forms overlap, generating moiré interference fields. Gold leaf accents at gravitational anchor points. At this dimension the work forces ambulatory engagement: you must walk along it, tracking the orbits. The overlapping circles create visual beats, interference patterns suggesting gravitational waves frozen mid-propagation.','Celestial Secrets',1,2,'2025-12-27 07:59:29','2026-02-12 15:47:31',0,'horizontal-orbital-mural-study-90002','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','Architectural cosmology that forces full-body engagement, tracking gravitational waves through the visual beats of overlapping circles.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90003,'Yin-yang Gold Disc',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','balanced duality','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0013(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0013(1).jpg','Vertical yin-yang structure. Large gold disc at center surrounded by dense ink spheres. Two smaller gold voids nested within the larger field. The composition oscillates between Eastern cosmology and Western astronomy.','Vertical yin-yang structure. Large gold disc at center within dense ink field. The yin-yang is not drawn but implied: negative space between ink and gold creates the curve. East-West synthesis at the structural level, the underlying unity of traditions revealed through the gap between materials. Fusion not illustrated. Enacted.','Celestial Secrets',1,3,'2025-12-27 07:59:31','2026-02-12 15:47:31',0,'yin-yang-gold-disc-90003','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','A structural fusion of traditions where the negative space between ink and gold implies the underlying unity of Eastern and Western thought.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90004,'Vertical Cross with Gold Satellites',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','vertical transmission','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0011(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0011(1).jpg','Vertical emphasis. Large central ink sphere flanked by gold leaf circles at cardinal points. Smaller ink satellites orbit at intermediate positions. The composition reads as both crucifix and antenna—spiritual and technological simultaneously.','Strong vertical emphasis. Large central ink sphere flanked by gold leaf at cardinal points. The composition reads simultaneously as crucifix and antenna: spiritual and technological. The collision point where spiritual geometry and physical cosmology become indistinguishable. Sacred technology.','Celestial Secrets',1,4,'2025-12-27 07:59:33','2026-02-12 15:47:32',0,'vertical-cross-with-gold-satellites-90004','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','The collision of spiritual geometry and physical cosmology, where the crucifix and the antenna become indistinguishable.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90005,'Orbital Installation View',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','600cm x 150cm','Black, Gold, White','immersive installation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/DSC07648~2.jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/DSC07648~2.jpg','Installation view at West Eden Gallery. The viewer stands before the work at human scale. The overlapping circular forms create depth and movement. The moiré interference suggests vibration, resonance.','Installation documentation at West Eden Gallery. The viewer at human scale. Phenomenological immersion: at this dimension the work becomes environment. The viewer is inside the orbital system, not observing from outside. The shift from representation to experience.','Celestial Secrets',1,5,'2025-12-27 07:59:36','2026-02-12 15:47:32',0,'orbital-installation-view-90005','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','A shift from representation to environment, placing the viewer inside the resonance of an immersive orbital system.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90006,'Asymmetric Orbital Cluster',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','dynamic imbalance','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0016(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0016(1).jpg','Asymmetric composition. Gold leaf circles cluster on the right side, creating visual weight. Ink spheres provide counterbalance but the composition refuses perfect symmetry. This is orbital mechanics as improvisation.','Gold leaf circles cluster asymmetrically, creating visual weight. Ink spheres counterbalance but the composition refuses perfect symmetry. Unlike the calculated precision of earlier phases, this work registers as intuitive, responsive. The asymmetry is evidence of surrender. The artist is facilitating rather than controlling. Conduit consciousness made visible.','Celestial Secrets',1,6,'2025-12-27 07:59:38','2026-02-12 15:47:33',0,'asymmetric-orbital-cluster-90006','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','Evidence of surrender to intuition, where the refusal of perfect symmetry marks the artist as a facilitator rather than a controller.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90007,'Gold Crescent Orbit',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','lunar phase','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0014(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0014(1).jpg','Large gold crescent forms orbit around central ink sphere. The crescent suggests lunar phase, waxing or waning. Smaller satellites complete the orbital field. The work oscillates between astronomical diagram and alchemical symbol.','Large gold crescent forms orbit central ink sphere. The crescent invokes both lunar phase and alchemical symbol: the lunar principle, the feminine, the receptive. But also literal: a satellite\'s orbit captured mid-rotation. Alchemy and astronomy occupy the same coordinate.','Celestial Secrets',1,7,'2025-12-27 07:59:40','2026-02-12 15:47:33',0,'gold-crescent-orbit-90007','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','Alchemical astronomy that captures the lunar principle as both a receptive symbol and a literal planet mid-rotation.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90008,'Vertical Axis with Gold Poles',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','polar alignment','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0015(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0015(1).jpg','Strong vertical axis. Small gold circles at top and bottom poles. Larger ink spheres occupy the central band with intermediate gold accents. The composition reads as axis mundi—world axis connecting heaven and earth.','Strong vertical axis with small gold circles at top and bottom poles. Larger ink spheres in the central band. The axis mundi: world-axis connecting above and below, transcendent and material. The cosmological spine drawn as transmission beam.','Celestial Secrets',1,8,'2025-12-27 07:59:41','2026-02-12 15:47:34',0,'vertical-axis-with-gold-poles-90008','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','A cosmological spine connecting heaven and earth, framing the structure of the universe as a transmission beam.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90009,'Dense Cross Mandala',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','saturated symmetry','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0017(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0017(1).jpg','Dense cross mandala. Central sphere surrounded by tightly packed orbital rings. Gold leaf accents at cardinal and intercardinal points. The moiré density approaches saturation—the work vibrates at high frequency.','Central sphere surrounded by tightly packed orbital rings. Gold leaf at cardinal and intercardinal points. Moiré density approaching saturation: almost too much visual information for the eye to process. Signal saturation. Chaos at such high intensity it begins to simulate order.','Celestial Secrets',1,9,'2025-12-27 07:59:43','2026-02-12 15:47:34',0,'dense-cross-mandala-90009','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','Signal saturation where the hexagonal storm principle transforms extreme chaos into a high-frequency ordered field.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(90010,'Spiral Galaxy S-curve',30006,'2023-06','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','30cm x 40cm','Black, Gold, White','galactic rotation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0018(1).jpg',NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/celestial-secrets/IMG-20230616-WA0018(1).jpg','S-curve composition. Ink and gold spheres arranged in spiral formation. The largest sphere anchors the center; smaller satellites trace the rotational path. This is the first explicit galaxy structure in the practice.','S-curve composition. Ink and gold spheres in spiral formation. The first explicit galaxy structure in the practice. The spiral is the shape of galaxies, hurricanes, DNA, nautilus shells: the universal pattern of growth and motion. By moving from circular to spiral, the practice shifts from static equilibrium to dynamic process.','Celestial Secrets',1,10,'2025-12-27 07:59:46','2026-02-12 15:47:34',0,'spiral-galaxy-s-curve-90010','Ink and metallic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2023','A shift from static equilibrium to dynamic process, adopting the spiral as the universal pattern of motion and growth.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120014,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 1',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','foundational tension','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825091966-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning1.jpg','works/ph1/1766825091966-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning1.jpg',NULL,'The first work of the series. The beginning of the dialogue between form and void.','The origin point. Patient zero. This work establishes the visual vocabulary that will define the entire first phase: the torus as consciousness, the black element as the Absurd. The beginning of a dialogue between form and void that will persist across seven years and five phases. Everything starts here.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,1,'2025-12-27 08:45:00','2026-02-12 15:47:35',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-1-120014','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The origin point of the visual vocabulary, establishing the torus as consciousness and the black element as the Absurd.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120016,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 2',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','developing conflict','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825100649-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning2.jpg','works/ph1/1766825100649-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning2.jpg',NULL,'The dialogue continues. The geometry grows more complex as the conflict deepens.','Second iteration. The torus begins to fold and twist, introducing topological complexity as the existential question deepens. The geometry grows more intricate because the conflict demands it. Each iteration asks the same question from a different angle.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,2,'2025-12-27 08:45:05','2026-02-12 15:47:35',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-2-120016','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The second iteration where geometry begins to fold and twist, suggesting the growing complexity of the existential inquiry.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120021,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 3',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','existential tension','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825106028-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning3_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825106028-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning3_1_.jpg',NULL,'The circle strives for wholeness; the bar interrupts it. This is the core dialectic of the phase. I build the illusion of volume only to shatter it with the flat reality of the black bar.','The primary conflict crystallized. The circle strives for wholeness; the black bar interrupts it. The torus is the infinite loop of consciousness seeking meaning. The bar is the Absurd: the hard limit of the universe\'s indifference. The geometry tries to flow around the obstacle. The interruption is absolute. Core dialectic of the phase, stated without ambiguity.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,3,'2025-12-27 08:45:26','2026-02-12 15:47:36',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-3-120021','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The core dialectic of the phase: a torus representing the infinite loop of meaning is absolutely interrupted by the universe\'s indifference.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120028,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 4',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','deepening inquiry','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825126989-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning4_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825126989-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning4_1_.jpg',NULL,'The forms multiply. Each iteration asks the same question from a different angle.','Multiplication. Multiple torus forms interact for the first time, suggesting the existential question is not singular but fractal: each answer spawns new questions. The problem reproduces. What was dialogue becomes ecology.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,4,'2025-12-27 08:45:48','2026-02-12 15:47:36',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-4-120028','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A fractal multiplication of the existential question, where each answer spawns new geometric interactions.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120032,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 5',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','complex interruption','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825148901-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning5_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825148901-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning5_1_.jpg',NULL,'A complex knot, folded in on itself, interrupted by a horizontal bar. The thought process is denser here, but the censor is still present.','A complex knot folded in on itself, interrupted by a horizontal bar. The bar sits like a redaction over the dense geometry. No matter how intricate the reasoning, the silence of the universe remains the final word. The interruption is not proportional to the complexity beneath it. That disproportion is the point.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,5,'2025-12-27 08:46:09','2026-02-12 15:47:37',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-5-120032','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The horizontal bar acts as a final redaction over complex logic, asserting the silence of the universe as the ultimate word.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120033,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 6',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','infinite loop','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825169192-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning6.jpg','works/ph1/1766825169192-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning6.jpg',NULL,'The figure-eight torus. A continuous surface with no inside or outside. Hand-drawn micro-lines create a moiré field that vibrates.','The figure-eight torus. A continuous surface with no inside or outside. Hand-drawn micro-lines create a moiré field that pulses optically: the static image appears to breathe. The self-sustaining nature of the existential question feeding on itself endlessly. The moiré breath is the first instance of what will later become the practice\'s Respiratory Architecture.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,6,'2025-12-27 08:46:13','2026-02-12 15:47:37',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-6-120033','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The \"moiré breath\" creates an optical pulse, representing the self-sustaining nature of an endless existential inquiry.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120034,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 7',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','sustained inquiry','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825173449-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning7.jpg','works/ph1/1766825173449-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning7.jpg',NULL,'The series continues. Each work is a meditation on the same impossible question.','Seventh iteration. By this point the artist has established a rhythm of inquiry. The question does not resolve. It deepens. Persistence itself has become the subject.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,7,'2025-12-27 08:46:18','2026-02-12 15:47:37',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-7-120034','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The establishment of a rhythm of inquiry where the question does not resolve but deepens through iteration.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120035,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 8',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','asymmetrical cut','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825178772-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning8.jpg','works/ph1/1766825178772-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning8.jpg',NULL,'Variation on the interruption. The placement of the bar feels random, arbitrary. It strikes where it chooses.','Variation on the interruption. The bar\'s placement feels random, arbitrary: not structural but accidental. The Camusian register: the universe\'s silence is not malicious. It is indifferent. The geometry doesn\'t matter to the bar. The bar doesn\'t care where it falls.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,8,'2025-12-27 08:46:47','2026-02-12 15:47:38',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-8-120035','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The arbitrary limit of the Absurd is emphasized through a bar that strikes the geometry at an accidental, indifferent angle.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120036,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 9',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','approaching resolution','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825207823-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning9.jpg','works/ph1/1766825207823-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning9.jpg',NULL,'The forms begin to stabilize. Not resolution, but acceptance.','The forms begin to stabilize. Not resolution, but acceptance. The question has not been answered. The artist has learned to hold it without breaking. Approaching equilibrium with the unanswerable.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,9,'2025-12-27 08:47:18','2026-02-12 15:47:38',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-9-120036','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A stabilization of form suggesting that the artist has learned to hold the impossible question without breaking.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120037,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 10',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','sustained tension','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825239047-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning10.jpg','works/ph1/1766825239047-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning10.jpg',NULL,'The tenth iteration. The dialogue continues without resolution.','Tenth iteration. The series demonstrates that the existential question is not meant to be answered but inhabited. The practice of asking replaces the need for an answer. Sustained tension as method.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,10,'2025-12-27 08:47:22','2026-02-12 15:47:39',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-10-120037','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','Ten iterations prove that the existential question is intended to be inhabited rather than answered.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120038,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 11',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, White','heavy oppression','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825242802-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning11.jpg','works/ph1/1766825242802-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning11.jpg',NULL,'A massive black sphere rests atop a delicate torus. The visual weight is crushing. Gravity as an existential metaphor.','A massive black sphere atop a delicate torus. The visual weight is crushing. Unlike the bars which cut, this sphere presses down. The heavy, mute presence of the Absurd bearing down on the fragile structure of human logic. Gravity as existential metaphor. The torus holds. Barely.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,11,'2025-12-27 08:47:26','2026-02-12 15:47:39',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-11-120038','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The heavy, mute presence of the Absurd crushes the delicate structure of logic, moving from \"cut\" to \"weight.\"','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120039,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 12',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, White','dual eclipse','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825247073-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning12.jpg','works/ph1/1766825247073-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning12.jpg',NULL,'Variation on the sphere/torus interaction. The relationship feels celestial—an eclipse of meaning.','Sphere/torus interaction reads as celestial: an eclipse of meaning. The solid black form and the torus\'s central void align into a portrait of absence meeting absence. Two kinds of nothing in conversation.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,12,'2025-12-27 08:47:30','2026-02-12 15:47:40',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-12-120039','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A dual eclipse where the solid black form and the torus void align in a portrait of absence meeting absence.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120040,'Absurdity of Meaning No. 13',30001,'2018-03','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, White','culminating statement','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825250756-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning13_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825250756-peteryuill_absurdityofmeaning13_1_.jpg',NULL,'The final work of the core series. Not an ending, but a threshold.','Thirteenth work. Completion of the initial cycle. Not ending but threshold. The question remains open, but the vocabulary has been established. The artist can now say what he needs to say. The language exists. The conversation is not over. It is equipped.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,13,'2025-12-27 08:47:51','2026-02-12 15:47:40',0,'absurdity-of-meaning-no-13-120040','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The completion of the initial cycle, establishing the threshold for all subsequent geometric vocabulary.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120041,'Geometric Abstraction No. 4',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','pure form','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825271128-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_4_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825271128-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_4_1_.jpg',NULL,'The geometry without the conflict. Pure form, pure line, pure meditation.','The geometry without the conflict. Pure form, pure line, pure meditation. Without the black bars, the torus exists in a state of pure potential. Geometry before the fall. Evidence that the form itself, prior to the Absurdist intervention, carries its own quiet charge.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,14,'2025-12-27 08:48:17','2026-02-12 15:47:41',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-4-120041','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','Geometry before the fall, where the torus exists in a state of pure potential without the conflict of the black bar.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120042,'Geometric Abstraction No. 5',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','expanding complexity','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825297824-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_5_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825297824-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_5_1_.jpg',NULL,'The forms grow more complex. Each line is a decision, each curve a commitment.','Forms grow more complex. Each line a decision, each curve a commitment. The density of hand-drawn lines demonstrates the no-undo discipline: every stroke permanent, every decision irreversible. The accumulation of commitment made visible.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,15,'2025-12-27 08:48:40','2026-02-12 15:47:41',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-5-120042','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The \"no-undo\" discipline is literalized in the density of lines, marking each stroke as an irreversible decision.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120043,'Geometric Abstraction No. 6',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','topological fold','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825321119-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_6_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825321119-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_6_1_.jpg',NULL,'A folded torus, revealing the \"saddle\" geometry. The lines cross and weave, creating a fabric of ink.','A folded torus revealing saddle geometry. Lines cross and weave, creating a fabric of ink. A map of a thought turning back on itself. The complexity of the fold documents the topology of recursive consciousness while demonstrating technical mastery of the hand-drawn algorithm.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,16,'2025-12-27 08:48:45','2026-02-12 15:47:41',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-6-120043','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','Technical mastery of the hand-drawn algorithm creates a fabric of logic where the geometry turns back on itself.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120044,'Geometric Abstraction No. 7',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','sustained precision','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825325436-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_7_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825325436-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_7_1_.jpg',NULL,'The discipline continues. Hours of hand-drawn lines accumulate into form.','Hours of hand-drawn lines accumulate into form. The discipline continues. The form emerges from sustained labor, not despite it. Each work represents a meditative session measured in hours. The practice is the product.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,17,'2025-12-27 08:48:50','2026-02-12 15:47:42',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-7-120044','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','Form emerges from hours of meditative labor, where the discipline of accumulation becomes the work itself.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120045,'Geometric Abstraction No. 8',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','deepening density','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825330777-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_8_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825330777-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_8_1_.jpg',NULL,'The line density increases. The moiré effect intensifies.','Line density increases. The moiré effect intensifies. As strokes accumulate beyond a certain threshold, the static image begins to breathe. The optical vibration is emergent: no individual line causes it. The aggregate does. System behavior that no single element can produce.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,18,'2025-12-27 08:48:56','2026-02-12 15:47:42',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-8-120045','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','An intensification of line density that causes the static image to breathe through the moiré effect.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120046,'Geometric Abstraction No. 9',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','high-frequency moiré','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825336740-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_9_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825336740-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_9_1_.jpg',NULL,'Dense concentric torus. The line density is extremely high, creating intense optical vibration.','Dense concentric torus. Line density reaches critical mass where individual strokes disappear and become a field of frequency. Visual resonance: geometry aspiring to the condition of sound. The hum. You can almost hear it.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,19,'2025-12-27 08:49:03','2026-02-12 15:47:43',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-9-120046','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','Individual strokes disappear into a field of visual resonance, where geometry aspires to the condition of sound.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120047,'Geometric Abstraction No. 10',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','approaching transcendence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825343129-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_10_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825343129-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_10_1_.jpg',NULL,'The forms begin to suggest something beyond themselves.','At this density, the geometry begins to suggest something beyond pure form: a portal, a frequency, a state of mind. The line-work has crossed a threshold where representation of the torus yields to activation of the field. The suggestion of elsewhere.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,20,'2025-12-27 08:49:08','2026-02-12 15:47:43',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-10-120047','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The high density of form begins to suggest a portal or a transcendent state of mind.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120048,'Geometric Abstraction No. 11',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','56cm x 76cm','Black, White','near-completion','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825348941-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_11.jpg','works/ph1/1766825348941-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_11.jpg',NULL,'The series approaches its end. The vocabulary is complete.','The geometric vocabulary approaches completion. The series nears its end, not through exhaustion but through having established the full range of the formal language. Everything that follows across all subsequent phases will draw on what was built here.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,21,'2025-12-27 08:49:12','2026-02-12 15:47:44',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-11-120048','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The culmination of a geometric vocabulary that will serve as the foundation for the entire seven-year cosmology.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120049,'Geometric Abstraction No. 12',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, White','vertical totem','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825352133-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_12.jpg','works/ph1/1766825352133-peteryuill_geometricabstraction_12.jpg',NULL,'Vertical arrangement of torus forms. A totem of pure geometry.','Vertical arrangement of torus forms. A totem of pure geometry. Verticality suggests hierarchy or spine. Even without the absurdist bars, the structure feels precarious: balanced on a razor\'s edge of precision. The geometry holds because the hand held.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,22,'2025-12-27 08:49:15','2026-02-12 15:47:44',0,'geometric-abstraction-no-12-120049','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A totem of pure geometry that stands on a razor\'s edge of precision, suggesting a vertical hierarchy','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120051,'Mathematical Meditation No. 1',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','50cm x 50cm','Black, White','contemplative violence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825355355-peteryuill_mathematicalmeditation1_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825355355-peteryuill_mathematicalmeditation1_1_.jpg',NULL,'The first of the meditations. Mathematics as a form of prayer.','The title is deliberately paradoxical: mathematics as meditation, logic as devotion. Square format. The work attempts to reconcile rational structure with spiritual practice. The first of the meditations. The prayer begins.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,23,'2025-12-27 08:49:24','2026-02-12 15:47:45',0,'mathematical-meditation-no-1-120051','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A paradoxical attempt to reconcile the rational and the spiritual, framing logic as a form of prayer.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120053,'Mathematical Meditation No. 2',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','76cm x 56cm','Black, White','violent redaction','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825364852-peteryuill_mathematicalmeditation2_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825364852-peteryuill_mathematicalmeditation2_1_.jpg',NULL,'A torus slashed by multiple aggressive black bars—diagonal and vertical. The violence is palpable.','The most aggressive work of the PH1 set. A torus slashed by multiple black bars, diagonal and vertical. The bars do not merely interrupt; they attack. The frustration of the seeker visualized: the answer is not just missing. It is actively withheld.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,24,'2025-12-27 08:49:30','2026-02-12 15:47:45',0,'mathematical-meditation-no-2-120053','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A visualization of the seeker\'s frustration, where black bars aggressively withhold the answers from the geometric structure.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120055,'There Lay an Invincible Summer',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','120cm x 120cm','Black, White','defiant hope','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825370507-peteryuill_there_lay_an_invincible_summer.jpg','works/ph1/1766825370507-peteryuill_there_lay_an_invincible_summer.jpg',NULL,'From Camus: \"In the midst of winter, I found there was, within me, an invincible summer.\" The title is a declaration of survival.','From Camus: \"In the midst of winter, I found there was, within me, an invincible summer.\" The title is a declaration of survival. This work marks the pivot from questioning to affirming. The Absurd remains. So does the will to create despite it. 120cm square. Defiance codified in geometry.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,25,'2025-12-27 08:49:52','2026-02-12 15:47:45',0,'there-lay-an-invincible-summer-120055','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','A declaration of survival and the will to create despite the winter of the Absurd.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120056,'I Wonder If I Really Exist',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','120cm x 160cm','Black, White','existential doubt','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825393028-peteryuill_iwonderifireallyexist_1_.jpg','works/ph1/1766825393028-peteryuill_iwonderifireallyexist_1_.jpg',NULL,'The fundamental question. Not \"what is the meaning of life?\" but \"am I even here to ask?\"','The fundamental question stripped to its most basic form. Not \"what is the meaning of life?\" but \"am I even here to ask?\" Before meaning, before purpose: existence itself is uncertain. 120cm × 160cm. The largest work in PH1. The doubt required scale.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,26,'2025-12-27 08:49:56','2026-02-12 15:47:46',0,'i-wonder-if-i-really-exist-120056','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The fundamental doubt that strips the existential question down to the uncertainty of existence itself','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(120057,'Theatre of Memory',30001,'2018','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','120cm x 120cm','Black, White','mnemonic architecture','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1/1766825397041-peteryuill_theatre_of_memory.jpg','works/ph1/1766825397041-peteryuill_theatre_of_memory.jpg',NULL,'Reference to Giulio Camillo\'s memory palace. The geometry as a container for thought.','Reference to Giulio Camillo\'s memory palace. The geometry as architectural container for thought. The torus becomes a mnemonic structure: a Renaissance memory palace built from ink lines. The architecture of consciousness. Thought housed in form.','Absurdity of Meaning',1,27,'2025-12-27 08:50:02','2026-02-12 15:47:46',0,'theatre-of-memory-120057','Ink and acrylic paint on Saunders Waterford 300gsm hot press cotton rag paper','2018','The torus as a container for thought, referencing the Renaissance tradition of organizing knowledge within architectural structures','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150001,'Constructivist Composition with Burnt Orange Bar',30002,'2018-06','Ink and acrylic on canvas','200cm x 150cm','Black, White, Burnt Orange','dynamic tension','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/sp_peteryuill_com.jpg','works/ph1a/sp_peteryuill_com.jpg',NULL,'The burnt orange bar was a site-specific adaptation — the client wanted warmth to match the interior. I drew from Constructivist precedents, allowing the bars to collide at angles rather than remain rectilinear.','The first warm color in the practice. Burnt orange is not spiritual gold or grounding copper; it is architectural color, adapted to match corporate interiors. The Constructivist arrangement references Russian avant-garde geometry as revolutionary architecture. Bars collide at angles rather than remaining rectilinear. The existential vocabulary deployed into commercial space for the first time.','Institutional Commissions',1,1,'2025-12-27 12:00:30','2026-02-12 15:47:47',0,'constructivist-composition-with-burnt-orange-bar-150001','Ink and acrylic on canvas','2018','⁷The first introduction of architectural color, using Russian avant-garde precedents to collide geometry at angles.','[\"Ink\"]'),(150002,'Torus No. 1 (soho House Commission)',30002,'2018-08','Ink, gold leaf, and copper leaf on mounted paper','150cm x 100cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','alchemical duality','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/torus_1_soho_house_peteryuill.jpg','works/ph1a/torus_1_soho_house_peteryuill.jpg',NULL,'The gold and copper bars side by side — this was the first time I explicitly coded the binary. Gold (solar, spiritual, transcendent) and copper (earthly, grounding, embodied). The torus moves between them as a continuous current.','The gold-copper binary crystallized. Two metallic bars side by side, functioning as energetic poles: gold (solar, spiritual, transcendent) and copper (earthly, grounding, embodied). The torus moves between them as a continuous current. Not decoration. Alchemical coding installed in a members\' club.','Institutional Commissions',1,2,'2025-12-27 12:00:32','2026-02-12 15:47:47',0,'torus-no-1-soho-house-commission-150002','Ink, gold leaf, and copper leaf on mounted paper','2018','The gold-copper binary is crystallized for the first time, establishing the alchemical current between solar and earthly poles.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150003,'Torus No. 2 (soho House Commission, Copper Grounding)',30002,'2018-09','Ink and copper leaf on mounted paper','150cm x 100cm','Black, White, Copper','grounded foundation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/torus_2_soho_house-peteryuill.jpg','works/ph1a/torus_2_soho_house-peteryuill.jpg',NULL,'The copper plane covering the lower third — this was about grounding. The torus (eternal, celestial) rests on copper (earthly, temporal). Transcendence requires a foundation. You cannot ascend without being rooted.','Copper plane covering the lower third. The torus rests on copper: the eternal on the temporal. Transcendence requires foundation. You cannot ascend without being rooted. The inverted hierarchy of spiritual abstraction: the ground comes first.','Institutional Commissions',1,3,'2025-12-27 12:00:32','2026-02-12 15:47:48',0,'torus-no-2-soho-house-commission-copper-grounding-150003','Ink and copper leaf on mounted paper','2018','An inversion of spiritual hierarchy where the copper floor provides the necessary foundation for the torus to stand.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150004,'Torus No. 3 (yin-yang Composition with Gold Plane)',30002,'2018-11','Ink and gold leaf on paper','80cm x 80cm','Black, White, Gold','cosmological balance','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/torus_3_peteryuill_1.jpg','works/ph1a/torus_3_peteryuill_1.jpg',NULL,'The figure-eight torus with a gold plane covering half the composition — this was my attempt to visualize the Taoist yin-yang principle through Western geometric abstraction. Opposites interpenetrate.','Figure-eight torus with gold plane covering half the composition. Taoist yin-yang principle rendered through Western geometric abstraction. Opposites interpenetrate. The gold is not covering the geometry; it is completing it. East-West synthesis enacted at the structural level.','Institutional Commissions',1,4,'2025-12-27 12:00:33','2026-02-12 15:47:48',0,'torus-no-3-yin-yang-composition-with-gold-plane-150004','Ink and gold leaf on paper','2018','Western geometric abstraction is used to literalize Taoist principles, showing that opposites interpenetrate to complete the whole.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150005,'Torus No. 4 (dual-torus Chain with Gold Accent)',30002,'2019-01','Ink and gold leaf on paper','100cm x 100cm','Black, White, Gold','systemic flow','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/torus_4_peteryuill.jpg','works/ph1a/torus_4_peteryuill.jpg',NULL,'Two interlocking tori, linked in a continuous chain. The gold bar marks a specific point in the flow — a caesura, a threshold. This was when I started thinking about geometry as network, not just isolated form.','Two interlocking tori linked in continuous chain. Gold bar marks a specific point in the flow: a caesura, a threshold. The introduction of multiplicity. Geometry as network, not isolated form. The shift from existential rupture toward systemic thinking. The gold doesn\'t shatter. It highlights.','Institutional Commissions',1,5,'2025-12-27 12:00:34','2026-02-12 15:47:48',0,'torus-no-4-dual-torus-chain-with-gold-accent-150005','Ink and gold leaf on paper','2019','A shift from existential rupture to systemic thinking, where geometry is framed as a network of interlocking forms.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150006,'Peninsula Hotels Installation View 1',30002,'2019-03','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 300cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','institutional presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_1.jpg','works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_1.jpg',NULL,'Installed at Peninsula Hotels. The works function as threshold markers — elevator lobbies, suite entrances. They had to hold their ground in high-traffic, brightly-lit spaces. The geometry becomes ambient presence, not demanding attention but offering depth to those who pause.','The institutional test. The geometry is no longer private studio work; it is public architecture. Threshold markers in elevator lobbies and suite entrances. Thousands of people walk past. Most will not stop. The works do not need to be understood to be real. Their presence is the point.','Institutional Commissions',1,6,'2025-12-27 12:00:34','2026-02-12 15:47:49',0,'peninsula-hotels-installation-view-1-150006','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Geometry as ambient threshold markers that offer depth to those who pause in high-traffic institutional spaces.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150007,'Peninsula Hotels Installation View 2',30002,'2019-03','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 300cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','institutional presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_2.jpg','works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_2.jpg',NULL,'Same installation, different angle. The exposed ductwork and industrial ceiling contrast with the precision of the geometry. The work absorbs the architectural context without being diminished by it.','Installation documentation, alternate angle. Moiré patterns created by dense micro-lines change as the viewer moves. The works appear to breathe, pulse, rotate. Time-based abstraction in a static medium: the work unfolds over duration, not in a single glance. Industrial ceiling contrasts the geometry\'s precision without diminishing it.','Institutional Commissions',1,7,'2025-12-27 12:00:35','2026-02-12 15:47:49',0,'peninsula-hotels-installation-view-2-150007','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Time-based abstraction where the breathing moiré patterns unfold over duration as the viewer moves.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150008,'Peninsula Hotels Installation View 3',30002,'2019-03','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 300cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','institutional presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_3.jpg','works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_3.jpg',NULL,'The natural light from the windows changes how the gold and copper read throughout the day. The works are temporally alive — they look different at dawn, noon, dusk.','Natural light from windows alters how gold and copper read throughout the day. The works are temporally alive: different at dawn, noon, dusk. Phenomenological installation functioning at multiple scales. Close-up: hand-drawn micro-lines visible. Mid-range: composition reads as whole. Far view: work functions as architectural element.','Institutional Commissions',1,8,'2025-12-27 12:00:36','2026-02-12 15:47:50',0,'peninsula-hotels-installation-view-3-150008','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Temporally alive works that function at multiple scales, from hand-drawn micro-lines to architectural elements.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150009,'Peninsula Hotels Installation View 4',30002,'2019-03','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 300cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','institutional presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_4.jpg','works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_4.jpg',NULL,'Close-up view showing the density of the hand-drawn lines. Each work required 40–80 hours of labor. The no-undo constraint creates psychological presence — each line carries weight.','Close-up revealing the density of hand-drawn lines. 40-80 hours of labor per work. The no-undo constraint creates psychological presence: each line carries weight. Slight variations in line weight, subtle misalignments. The tension between aspiration (mathematical perfection) and reality (human fallibility). The hand is never invisible.','Institutional Commissions',1,9,'2025-12-27 12:00:37','2026-02-12 15:47:50',0,'peninsula-hotels-installation-view-4-150009','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','The tension between mathematical aspiration and human fallibility is made visible through the visible touch of the hand at scale.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150010,'Peninsula Hotels Installation View 5',30002,'2019-03','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 300cm','Black, White, Gold, Copper','institutional presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_5.jpg','works/ph1a/Peninsula_hotel_5.jpg',NULL,'The Eames chairs and wooden table create a mid-century modern aesthetic. The geometry complements that — it is rigorous, disciplined, functional, but also spiritually resonant.','Eames chairs and wooden table create mid-century modern context. The geometry is rigorous, disciplined, functional, while carrying spiritual resonance the furniture does not. The works do not compete with the space. They provide depth to those who pause. Ambient contemplation.','Institutional Commissions',1,10,'2025-12-27 12:00:38','2026-02-12 15:47:51',0,'peninsula-hotels-installation-view-5-150010','Ink, gold, and copper on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Disciplined geometry complements modern architecture, providing a spiritually resonant depth to functional space.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150011,'Kith & Kin Mural Installation 1',30002,'2019-04','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','500cm x 300cm','Black, White','architectural integration','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural1_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural1_2019.jpg',NULL,'The Kith & Kin commission required the geometry to work at monumental scale on a wall. The circular forms had to hold their ground against the architecture, becoming part of the building\'s visual language.','The geometry scales to architectural dimensions. The black-and-white vocabulary proves it can function as permanent architectural element. Circular forms hold their ground against the building, becoming part of its visual language. Not art on a wall. Art as wall.','Institutional Commissions',1,11,'2025-12-27 12:00:38','2026-02-12 15:47:51',0,'kith-kin-mural-installation-1-150011','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','2019','The black-and-white vocabulary scales to monumental dimensions, becoming a permanent architectural element of the building.','[\"Ink\"]'),(150012,'Kith & Kin Mural Installation 2',30002,'2019-04','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','500cm x 300cm','Black, White','architectural integration','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural2_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural2_2019.jpg',NULL,'Different angle showing how the mural interacts with the lighting and spatial context. The geometry creates depth on a flat wall, suggesting dimensionality where there is none.','The mural creates optical depth on a flat surface through dense line-work. Moiré patterns shift as viewers move through the space, creating time-based experience within static medium. Dimensionality suggested where none exists.','Institutional Commissions',1,12,'2025-12-27 12:00:39','2026-02-12 15:47:52',0,'kith-kin-mural-installation-2-150012','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','2019','Dense line-work suggests dimensionality on a flat wall, creating a shifting experience for viewers in motion.','[\"Ink\"]'),(150013,'Kith & Kin Mural Installation 3',30002,'2019-04','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','500cm x 300cm','Black, White','architectural integration','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural3_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Keith&kin_mural3_2019.jpg',NULL,'The full view showing the mural in its architectural context. The circular forms create a focal point in the space, drawing the eye and anchoring the room\'s visual hierarchy.','Full view in architectural context. The circular forms create a center of gravity in the space, organizing the visual field around their mass. The work anchors the room\'s hierarchy. Architecture defers to the geometry.','Institutional Commissions',1,13,'2025-12-27 12:00:40','2026-02-12 15:47:52',0,'kith-kin-mural-installation-3-150013','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','2019','Circular forms organize the visual field of the room, acting as an architectural anchor and center of gravity.','[\"Ink\"]'),(150014,'Kith & Kin Mural Installation 4',30002,'2019-04','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','500cm x 300cm','Black, White','architectural integration','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Kith&kin_mural4_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Kith&kin_mural4_2019.jpg',NULL,'Detail view showing the precision of the hand-painted lines at monumental scale. The no-undo constraint applies even to wall murals — each line is permanent, irreversible.','Detail view. Hand-painted precision maintained at monumental scale. The no-undo constraint applies even to permanent wall murals. Each line irreversible. The discipline documented at closest possible range.','Institutional Commissions',1,14,'2025-12-27 12:00:40','2026-02-12 15:47:52',0,'kith-kin-mural-installation-4-150014','Acrylic and ink on wall (large-scale mural)','2019','The psychological weight of the no-undo constraint is maintained even at an architectural scale.','[\"Ink\"]'),(150015,'Jll Corporate Installation',30002,'2019-05','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 150cm','Black, White','corporate contemplation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/JLL_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/JLL_2019.jpg',NULL,'The JLL commission tested whether existential abstraction could survive in a corporate real estate context. The geometry had to function in a space of commerce and transaction, not contemplation.','The test of whether existential abstraction survives corporate real estate context. The geometry holds ground in a space of commerce and transaction, providing contemplative depth in an environment typically devoid of spiritual resonance. Philosophy survives commerce. The work does not explain itself. It persists.','Institutional Commissions',1,15,'2025-12-27 12:00:41','2026-02-12 15:47:53',0,'jll-corporate-installation-150015','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Existential abstraction holds its ground in a space of commerce, providing contemplative depth where it is typically absent.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150016,'Nuva Airport Installation',30002,'2019-06','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 150cm','Black, White','threshold presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Nuva-airport_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Nuva-airport_2019.jpg',NULL,'The NUVA commission placed the work in a luxury brand space near the airport. The geometry had to function as threshold marker — signaling transition from public transit to private luxury.','The work placed in threshold space near the airport. The geometry functions as portal marker: signaling transition from public transit to private luxury. Circular forms create a moment of pause in a space designed for movement. The threshold is the content.','Institutional Commissions',1,16,'2025-12-27 12:00:42','2026-02-12 15:47:53',0,'nuva-airport-installation-150016','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','The geometry signals the transition from public transit to private luxury, acting as a portal marker in a threshold space.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150017,'Airport Restaurant Installation',30002,'2019-06','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 150cm','Black, White','ambient presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Airport_restaurnt_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Airport_restaurnt_2019.jpg',NULL,'Installed in an airport restaurant. The work had to function in a space of transience — people eating quickly before flights, distracted, anxious. The geometry offers a moment of stillness.','Installed in a space of transience. People eating quickly before flights, distracted, anxious. The geometry offers stillness. It does not demand attention. It offers it to those who look. Contemplative presence deployed into ambient noise.','Institutional Commissions',1,17,'2025-12-27 12:00:43','2026-02-12 15:47:54',0,'airport-restaurant-installation-150017','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','A moment of stillness offered to travelers in motion, providing depth within a space of transience.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150018,'Shenzhen Hotel Installation 1',30002,'2019-07','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 150cm','Black, White','cross-border presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Shenzen_hotel1_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Shenzen_hotel1_2019.jpg',NULL,'The Shenzhen commission marked the first time the work crossed into mainland China. The geometry had to function in a different cultural context — still Hong Kong-adjacent, but distinctly mainland.','The first time the practice crosses into mainland China. The geometry maintains conceptual integrity in a different cultural context. The forms prove they can travel without losing signal strength. The practice crosses the border.','Institutional Commissions',1,18,'2025-12-27 12:00:43','2026-02-12 15:47:54',0,'shenzhen-hotel-installation-1-150018','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','The practice crosses the border, proving the geometry’s conceptual integrity can survive new cultural and institutional contexts.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150019,'Shenzhen Hotel Installation 2',30002,'2019-07','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','200cm x 150cm','Black, White','cross-border presence','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Shenzen_hotel3_2019.jpg','works/ph1a/Shenzen_hotel3_2019.jpg',NULL,'Different view of the Shenzhen installation. The hotel\'s modern interior provides a clean backdrop for the geometry, allowing the forms to read clearly against neutral walls.','Alternate angle of the Shenzhen installation. Modern interior provides clean backdrop, allowing forms to read clearly. The visual language adapts to new architectural and cultural environments without degradation.','Institutional Commissions',1,19,'2025-12-27 12:00:44','2026-02-12 15:47:55',0,'shenzhen-hotel-installation-2-150019','Ink on mounted paper (large-scale)','2019','Clean modern interiors allow the geometric forms to read as a clear visual language in a mainland Chinese context.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(150020,'Justin Tan Private Commission',30002,'2018-12','Ink and gold leaf on paper','100cm x 80cm','Black, White, Gold','private contemplation','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph1a/Justin_tan_2018.jpg','works/ph1a/Justin_tan_2018.jpg',NULL,'A private commission for a collector. The work had to function in a domestic context — a home, not a gallery or hotel. The geometry becomes intimate, personal, a daily presence.','The geometry enters private domestic space. A daily contemplative presence for a collector. The practice scales from monumental institutional installations to intimate personal commissions. The work functions differently in a home: it is lived with, not visited. Proximity over duration.','Institutional Commissions',1,20,'2025-12-27 12:00:45','2026-02-12 15:47:55',0,'justin-tan-private-commission-150020','Ink and gold leaf on paper','2018','The practice scales to an intimate personal commission, becoming a daily contemplative presence in a domestic home.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180001,'Ink Storm (ascension)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','ascending energy','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/IMG_0386.jpg','works/ph4/IMG_0386.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Ascending dragon-like stroke with heavy splatter and vertical energy. The ink rises against gravity, defying the pull of despair that characterized the Vietnam period. Painted during PH4 nomadic fieldwork, the work abandons geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release. A moment of lift within the storm. The body that made this was not thinking. It was throwing.','Ink Storms',1,13,'2025-12-27 13:29:38','2026-02-12 15:47:56',0,'ink-storm-ascension-180001','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','Nomadic fieldwork abandons geometric precision for high-velocity atmospheric pressure and somatic release.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180002,'Ink Storm (diagonal 01)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','diagonal impact','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240726_162209.jpg','works/ph4/20240726_162209.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Diagonal impact with heavy Bone-black cutting through white negative space. The composition suggests a body in motion: falling or flying, the distinction no longer mattering in the storm. The brush moved before the decision was made.','Ink Storms',1,14,'2025-12-27 13:29:53','2026-02-12 15:47:56',0,'ink-storm-diagonal-01-180002','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','A \"bone\" black cut through negative space suggests a body in motion, where the distinction between falling and flying is lost.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180003,'Ink Storm (mass)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','brooding density','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/2255.jpg','works/ph4/2255.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Massive central black density with wet bleed zones. The heaviest specimen in this batch: a visual anchor that absorbs light and attention. The storm at its most concentrated, most oppressive. Brooding density that refuses to disperse. The ink pooled and stayed.','Ink Storms',1,15,'2025-12-27 13:30:16','2026-02-12 15:47:56',0,'ink-storm-mass-180003','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','The storm at its most concentrated, serving as a visual anchor that absorbs light and attention through brooding density.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180004,'Ink Storm (strike)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','high velocity','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/Painting_10.jpg','works/ph4/Painting_10.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Vertical strike with high-velocity splash dynamics. The brush moved faster than thought: pure somatic response to humidity and displacement. A ballistic event recorded in ink. The splatter pattern is forensic evidence of velocity.','Ink Storms',1,16,'2025-12-27 13:30:26','2026-02-12 15:47:57',0,'ink-storm-strike-180004','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','A vertical strike with high-velocity dynamics representing a pure somatic response to displacement and humidity.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180005,'Vietnam Horizon 01',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','100cm x 100cm','Black, grey, white','landscape split','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/Painting_9.jpg','works/ph4/Painting_9.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Two distinct lateral sweeps with a gap between them. Reads as landscape/sky split: the horizon line separating earth from air, past from future, self from dissolution. The gap is the work\'s center. What is absent defines what flanks it.','Ink Storms ',1,17,'2025-12-27 13:30:31','2026-02-12 15:47:57',0,'vietnam-horizon-01-180005','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','A horizon line that separates self from dissolution, reading as the landscape split between earth and air.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180006,'Ink Storm (sweep)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','singular motion','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_114217.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_114217.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Thick calligraphic sweep executed in a singular motion. The entire composition is one breath, one gesture, one decision made and committed to without revision. Single-stroke painting as existential commitment. No second pass. No correction.','Ink Storms',1,18,'2025-12-27 13:30:37','2026-02-12 15:47:58',0,'ink-storm-sweep-180006','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','A thick, calligraphic gesture executed in a singular breath, documenting a decision made and committed to without revision.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(180007,'Ink Storm (burst)',30007,'2024-05 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, grey, white','explosive chaos','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240701_095820.jpg','works/ph4/20240701_095820.jpg',NULL,'High-velocity ink weather. Painted during the PH4 nomadic fieldwork in Vietnam, these works abandon geometric precision for atmospheric pressure, humidity, and somatic release.','Explosive particulate matter with shrapnel splatter. The most chaotic specimen in this batch: internal weather made external, emotion atomized into ink particles. The brush did not merely touch the paper. It detonated against it.','Ink Storms',1,19,'2025-12-27 13:30:45','2026-02-12 15:47:58',0,'ink-storm-burst-180007','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','A visual record of internal weather made external, where emotion is atomized into explosive ink particles.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210001,'Purple Portal (vietnam 01)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','radial bloom','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240803_113029.jpg','works/ph4/20240803_113029.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','A radial bloom where gray wash feathers outward from a vivid purple core. After years of strict monochrome, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. The geometry tries to hold its shape against the chromatic flood. Not decorative color. Structural rupture. The first major reintroduction since 2018.','Ink Storms',1,32,'2025-12-27 13:53:13','2026-02-12 15:47:59',0,'purple-portal-vietnam-01-210001','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','After years of strict monochrome, a radial bloom from a purple core breaks the seal on structural color.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210002,'Wounded Portal (magenta)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','violent rupture','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/Painting_8.jpg','works/ph4/Painting_8.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','A gray radial field split by a violent magenta diagonal slash. The wound is the portal: color breaking through monochrome discipline like blood through skin. Rupture as access point. The discipline had to break for something new to enter.','Ink Storms',1,33,'2025-12-27 13:55:13','2026-02-12 15:47:59',0,'wounded-portal-magenta-210002','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The wound is the portal, with color breaking through the monochrome discipline like blood through skin.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210003,'Ink Storm (cyan & Magenta)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','destabilized energy','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240725_104225.jpg','works/ph4/20240725_104225.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','Gestural storm-body destabilized by cyan and magenta flares. The black mass can no longer contain the color: it erupts at the edges, chemical and psychedelic. The monochrome field is losing sovereignty. New frequencies forcing through the carbon barrier.','Ink Storms',1,34,'2025-12-27 13:56:29','2026-02-12 15:47:59',0,'ink-storm-cyan-magenta-210003','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Chemical flares of color destabilize the black mass, proving the gesture can no longer be contained by monochrome.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210004,'Ink Storm (purple Flare)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','afterburn eruption','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240728_102241.jpg','works/ph4/20240728_102241.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','Vertical black mass with purple afterburn eruption. The color appears as residue, as heat signature, as the emotional trace left behind after the gesture completes. Not color applied. Color released.','Ink Storms',1,35,'2025-12-27 13:57:33','2026-02-12 15:48:00',0,'ink-storm-purple-flare-210004','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Color appears as a heat signature or emotional residue, marking the trace left behind by the vertical gesture.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210006,'Cosmic Bloom (multi-ring)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','pulsing complexity','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240723_132742.jpg','works/ph4/20240723_132742.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','Complex multi-ring mandala pulsing with blue and pink internal light. The most structured work in this batch, showing the link to earlier phases before color broke the form. The mandala holds, but the light leaking through its rings suggests chromatic pressure from within.','Portals',1,36,'2025-12-27 13:58:39','2026-02-12 15:48:00',0,'cosmic-bloom-multi-ring-210006','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A link to earlier phases where a structured mandala pulses with internal light before color fully breaks the form.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210008,'Portal (nested Eye)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','looking back','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240717_142027.jpg','works/ph4/20240717_142027.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','A looking-back aperture with sharp black pupil and cyan/magenta iris. The portal has become an eye. The work watches you as you watch it. Reciprocal gaze. The void is not passive. It has acquired optics.','Portals',1,37,'2025-12-27 13:59:50','2026-02-12 15:48:01',0,'portal-nested-eye-210008','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The portal becomes an eye, transforming the work into an aperture that watches the viewer as they watch it.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210010,'Portal (bleed)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','dissolving form','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/Painting_7.jpg','works/ph4/Painting_7.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','Heavy black radial field dissolving into pools of cyan and purple. The geometry losing its battle with entropy: color seeping through every crack in the monochrome structure. Dissolution as revelation. What was sealed is now permeable.','Portals',1,38,'2025-12-27 14:00:51','2026-02-12 15:48:01',0,'portal-bleed-210010','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The geometry loses its battle with entropy, allowing cyan and purple pools to seep through the dissolving black field.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210015,'Ink Storm (chaos)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','maximum chaos','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240717_111943.jpg','works/ph4/20240717_111943.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','High-velocity chaotic gesture mixing black Chinese ink with Western color pigments. Maximum entropy. The most uncontrolled work in the Vietnam suite. Pure discharge without compositional governance. The signal has overwhelmed the receiver.','Ink Storms',1,39,'2025-12-27 14:03:01','2026-02-12 15:48:02',0,'ink-storm-chaos-210015','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','nInk Storm (chaos) Pure entropy visualized through the uncontrolled mixing of black Chinese ink and Western color pigments.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210017,'Cosmic Bloom (teal)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','atmospheric softness','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/Painting_6_1_.jpg','works/ph4/Painting_6_1_.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','Soft atmospheric portal with teal and magenta outer ring. The gentlest specimen in this batch: color as invitation rather than rupture. Where the storm works scream, this one breathes. A moment of rest in the turbulence.','Portals',1,40,'2025-12-27 14:04:02','2026-02-12 15:48:02',0,'cosmic-bloom-teal-210017','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024','The gentlest rupture in the Vietnam batch, where teal and magenta rings serve as a soft atmospheric invitation.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210018,'Horizon Portal (split)',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','divided consciousness','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240717_113214.jpg','works/ph4/20240717_113214.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','A centralized form divided by a horizon line: cyan below, magenta above. Earth and sky, past and future, self and dissolution split by a single axis. The split is clean. Two registers of consciousness held in a single frame.','Portals',1,41,'2025-12-27 14:04:05','2026-02-12 15:48:03',0,'horizon-portal-split-210018','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A centralized form divided by an axis of cyan and magenta, representing earth and sky or the split of consciousness.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210022,'I Think I Can',30007,'2024-07 to 2024-08','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','75cm x 75cm','Black, cyan, magenta, purple, teal','determined chaos','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/2024071IthinkIcan7_111833.jpg','works/ph4/2024071IthinkIcan7_111833.jpg',NULL,'The moment color breaks the geometry. After years of strict monochrome sacred geometry, the Vietnam fieldwork broke the seal on color. But this isn\'t decorative—it\'s structural.','The title embedded in the filename speaks to the psychological state of the Vietnam period: determination mixed with doubt, the mantra repeated while the ink flies. Chaos with a slogan. The work does not prove the claim. It documents the attempt.','Portals',1,42,'2025-12-27 14:07:16','2026-02-12 15:48:03',0,'i-think-i-can-210022','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A determined chaos where the title reflects the psychological mantra of survival and doubt during the Vietnam period.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210023,'Oculus (dilating Ring)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','dilating tension','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134825.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134825.jpg','A monochrome study in void-gazing, where a heavy ink ring acts as a dilating pupil watching back.','The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','A heavy black ink ring with serrated inner edge, reading as dilating pupil. The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single monolithic aperture. Void-gazing reduced to its essential mechanism. The eye of the storm, watching you as you watch it.','Oculus',1,20,'2025-12-27 14:09:49','2026-02-12 15:48:03',0,'oculus-dilating-ring-210023','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210024,'Oculus (eclipse)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','total occlusion','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111019.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111019.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Dense black void surrounding a central light aperture. Solar eclipse in ink. The moment before totality, or just after. The light persists at the center because the dark cannot quite close around it. Near-total occlusion with a residual core of resistance.','Oculus',1,21,'2025-12-27 14:09:50','2026-02-12 15:48:04',0,'oculus-eclipse-210024','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The moment before or after totality, where a dense black void surrounds a central light aperture.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210025,'Oculus (soft Focus)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','atmospheric dissolution','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134809.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134809.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Diffused atmospheric ring where ink wash blurs the boundary between form and void. The geometry losing its grip. Edges dissolve. The aperture refuses to declare itself with precision. Soft focus as epistemological condition: knowing without certainty.','Oculus',1,22,'2025-12-27 14:09:51','2026-02-12 15:48:04',0,'oculus-soft-focus-210025','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A diffused atmospheric ring where the boundary between form and void is blurred by the loss of geometric grip.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210026,'Oculus (concentric Pulse)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','radiating vibration','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134838.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134838.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Multiple concentric ink rings radiating outward, creating vibration effect. The aperture pulses, breathing in and out. Respiratory architecture at its most compressed. A diagram of rhythmic contraction and expansion. Systole and diastole in carbon.','Oculus',1,23,'2025-12-27 14:09:52','2026-02-12 15:48:05',0,'oculus-concentric-pulse-210026','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Multiple radiating rings create a vibration effect, simulating the aperture breathing in and out.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210027,'Oculus (horizon Split)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','divided consciousness','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111207.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111207.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Circular aperture bisected by a horizon line. Landscape logic merges with portal logic. Earth below, sky above, void in between. The horizon splits the eye into two registers of seeing.','Oculus',1,24,'2025-12-27 14:09:52','2026-02-12 15:48:05',0,'oculus-horizon-split-210027','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Portal logic merges with the landscape, using a horizon line to bisect the void between earth and sky.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210028,'Oculus (heavy Mass)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','gravitational weight','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111125.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111125.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Monolithic black ring with deep saturation dominating white space. The heaviest specimen in the Oculus series. Pure gravitational pull. Maximum density, maximum authority. The aperture barely survives the pressure of the surrounding dark.','Oculus',1,25,'2025-12-27 14:09:53','2026-02-12 15:48:06',0,'oculus-heavy-mass-210028','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Pure gravitational pull achieved through a monolithic black ring that dominates the white space.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210029,'Oculus (interior Tooth)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','jagged interior','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111153.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111153.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Aperture with jagged, tooth-like ink bleed on the interior edge. The void has teeth. It bites back. The portal is not passive passage. It has defenses. Or appetites.','Oculus',1,26,'2025-12-27 14:09:54','2026-02-12 15:48:06',0,'oculus-interior-tooth-210029','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','An aperture with a jagged interior edge, suggesting that the void has teeth and can bite back.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210030,'Oculus (wash Field)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','ghostly atmosphere','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134645.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134645.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Softer, wider ring where ink wash creates ghostly atmospheric field. The gentlest Oculus: more suggestion than statement. The aperture is present but whispered. A haunting rather than an assertion.','Oculus',1,27,'2025-12-27 14:09:55','2026-02-12 15:48:07',0,'oculus-wash-field-210030','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The gentlest suggestion of void-gazing, using a ghostly atmospheric wash to create a wider, softer ring.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210031,'Oculus (double Ring)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','nested depth','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134723.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134723.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Two distinct ink densities forming a nested aperture structure. Depth within depth. The portal has layers: you pass through one threshold only to encounter another. Recursive containment.','Oculus',1,28,'2025-12-27 14:09:56','2026-02-12 15:48:07',0,'oculus-double-ring-210031','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A nested structure of distinct ink densities that gives the portal multiple layers of depth','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210032,'Oculus (void Core)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','central darkness','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134708.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134708.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Nearly solid black field with small, sharp central aperture of light. The darkest Oculus. Almost total occlusion. The light that remains is not generous. It is a pinprick of survival. Minimal signal in maximum noise.','Oculus',1,29,'2025-12-27 14:09:57','2026-02-12 15:48:07',0,'oculus-void-core-210032','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','The darkest occlusion in the series, featuring a nearly solid black field with a sharp, small aperture of light.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210033,'Oculus (horizon Maw)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','consuming aperture','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134550.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134550.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Circular form split by dark horizon band, the aperture appearing to consume the light above. The maw opens. The Oculus at its most predatory: the void actively swallowing luminosity. Not passive absence. Active consumption.','Oculus',1,30,'2025-12-27 14:09:57','2026-02-12 15:48:08',0,'oculus-horizon-maw-210033','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','A consuming aperture split by a dark horizon band, appearing to devour the light above it.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210034,'Oculus (nested Eye)',30007,'2024-06','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','40cm x 40cm','Black, gray, white','watching depth','https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240630_134624.jpg','works/ph4/20240630_134624.jpg',NULL,'The Oculus series strips the mandala back to a single, monolithic black aperture. These are monochrome studies in void-gazing—heavy ink rings that act as portals, eclipses, or dilating pupils.','Concentric rings forming a nested eye structure with luminous core. The portal watches back. Always watching. The most explicitly ocular specimen in the series: iris, pupil, sclera all implied through ink density gradients. The work has acquired consciousness.','Oculus',1,31,'2025-12-27 14:09:58','2026-02-12 15:48:08',0,'oculus-nested-eye-210034','Chinese and Western Inks of Anhui Rice Paper','2024','Concentric rings forming a watching depth that insists the portal is always looking back.','[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210035,'Study (vertebral Form)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/vfd.jpg','works/ph4/vfd.jpg',NULL,NULL,'An early PH4 synthesis study. The vertebral structure suggests the body\'s skeletal architecture rendered in wash. Transitional specimen between the geometric precision of earlier phases and the somatic discharge of the Ink Storms. The spine as organizing principle.','Studies & Residuals',1,1,'2025-12-27 15:07:13','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'study-vertebral-form-210035','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210036,'Residual (heavy Mass)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240724_161520.jpg','works/ph4/20240724_161520.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Heavy ink residue from a completed gesture: what remains after the action. The mass is not composed but deposited. Gravity\'s receipt for energy expended.','Studies & Residuals',1,2,'2025-12-27 15:07:13','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'residual-heavy-mass-210036','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210037,'Residual (broken Loop)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240724_153159.jpg','works/ph4/20240724_153159.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. A circular gesture that failed to close: the loop broken, the orbit interrupted. The break is the content. What would have been a mandala became a fragment.','Studies & Residuals',1,3,'2025-12-27 15:07:13','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'residual-broken-loop-210037','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210038,'Residual (horizontal Mass)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240724_153120.jpg','works/ph4/20240724_153120.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Horizontal ink mass distributed across the longer axis. Landscape orientation. The sediment of a gesture that moved sideways rather than down.','Studies & Residuals',1,4,'2025-12-27 15:07:13','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'residual-horizontal-mass-210038','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210039,'Study (cellular Wash)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240801_112613.jpg','works/ph4/20240801_112613.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Cellular structures emerging from wash technique. The ink\'s natural behavior on Anhui paper produces biological-looking forms without biological intent. The paper\'s fiber topography directing ink into cell-like patterns. Material intelligence visible.','Studies & Residuals',1,5,'2025-12-27 15:07:14','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'study-cellular-wash-210039','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210040,'Study (soft Ring)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240801_113712.jpg','works/ph4/20240801_113712.jpg',NULL,NULL,'A soft atmospheric ring study. The aperture form in its most gentle iteration: edges dissolved by wash, center barely defined. The Oculus prototype before it hardened into the formal series.','Studies & Residuals',1,6,'2025-12-27 15:07:14','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'study-soft-ring-210040','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210041,'Study (dense Core)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','75cm x 75cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240801_113635.jpg','works/ph4/20240801_113635.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Dense central ink accumulation radiating outward. Core density study. Maximum concentration at center, dispersal at periphery. A compression specimen.','Studies & Residuals',1,7,'2025-12-27 15:07:14','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'study-dense-core-210041','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210042,'Vietnam Horizon (bar 01)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111657.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111657.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Horizontal bar bisecting the field. The PH1 vocabulary (the interrupting bar) resurfaces in PH4\'s material language. The Absurd returns, rendered in atmospheric wash rather than hard-edge acrylic. The same question, different weather.','Vietnam Horizons',1,8,'2025-12-27 15:07:14','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'vietnam-horizon-bar-01-210042','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210043,'Vietnam Horizon (bar 02)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_112123.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_112123.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Second horizontal bar study. Variation on the Vietnam Horizon protocol. The bar holds. The horizon persists.','Vietnam Horizons',1,9,'2025-12-27 15:07:15','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'vietnam-horizon-bar-02-210043','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210044,'Horizon (intersected)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111955.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111955.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. The horizon line is itself interrupted: intersected by a vertical or diagonal element. The bar that bisects is itself bisected. Recursion of interruption.','Vietnam Horizons',1,10,'2025-12-27 15:07:15','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'horizon-intersected-210044','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210045,'Study (wash Fragment)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240801_112932.jpg','works/ph4/20240801_112932.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Fragment of a larger wash gesture. The paper captured only part of the action. An excerpt, a forensic fragment of an event that exceeded the substrate.','Studies & Residuals',1,11,'2025-12-27 15:07:15','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'study-wash-fragment-210045','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(210046,'Vietnam Horizon (bar 03)',30007,'2024','Inks on Anhui rice paper','50cm x 100cm',NULL,NULL,'https://d2xsxph8kpxj0f.cloudfront.net/310519663243139088/ZLCef8c8rdYgPCof2teogL/works/ph4/20240629_111634.jpg','works/ph4/20240629_111634.jpg',NULL,NULL,'Rectangular format. Third bar study. The repetition is the method. Each bar is the same question asked to different paper, different humidity, different hour. The bar persists across all conditions.','Vietnam Horizons',1,12,'2025-12-27 15:07:15','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'vietnam-horizon-bar-03-210046','Inks on Anhui rice paper','2024',NULL,'[\"Ink\", \"Paper\"]'),(240002,'Tidal',30009,'2025-12','Acrylic Paint and Spray Paint on Raw Linen\n','300cm x 1000cm (7 separate panels arranged in an arc)','Copper, gold, cream, blue-black, burnt sienna, raw umber','Gravitas','https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663243139088/HBPLSsdFbphVwyis.jpg',NULL,'https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663243139088/HBPLSsdFbphVwyis.jpg','The commission asked for lunar phases. I gave them a breathing cycle. Seven panels curving around a rotunda—the architecture itself became the ribcage. Each crescent is a held breath; the central sphere exhales. Sumi ink on Anhui paper at this scale required the pendulum rig to swing for hours. I watched the lines accumulate like tides. The oculus above mirrors the central moon. I didn\'t plan that. The building knew.','Acrylic and spray paint on raw linen, 300cm × 1000cm across seven panels arranged in an arc within the Swire rotunda. Site-specific meditation on containment and release. The architecture itself becomes the ribcage. Each crescent is a held breath; the central sphere exhales. The pendulum rig swung for hours, lines accumulating like tides. Burnt sienna, raw umber, oxidized copper flanking panels are the lungs contracting. The central orb is the pause between inhale and exhale: the moment where nothing moves and everything is possible. Moiré interference patterns suggest harmonic resonance, sound made visible, time made tactile. The ceiling oculus mirrors the central moon. Not planned. The building knew. Monument-scale work pursued through fragile means. That tension is structural, not incidental.','Covenant',1,16,'2026-01-04 09:35:09','2026-02-12 15:48:14',1,'tidal-240002','Acrylic Paint and Spray Paint on Raw Linen','2025','A site-specific respiratory system where gravity as a collaborator ground the sky and completes the architectural circuit of the rotunda.',NULL),(270001,'Carbon Mural H-Code',30005,'2021-10','Acrylic paint on prepared concrete wall. ','600cm x 180cm',NULL,'Spatial dominance / harmonic containment','https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663243139088/AvlpgpAwaFZzvMwy.jpg',NULL,NULL,'They gave me a dead wall above a bar. I gave them an event horizon. The circles chain past the frame—there is no edge, only implication. The backlight turns every line into a shadow of something that isn\'t there. I painted at 3am when the venue was empty. The spray can hiss echoed off concrete. When I finished, I stood at the bar and watched the geometry breathe in the UV wash. It looked like a signal. Like something waiting to be received.','Acrylic and spray paint on wall, 600cm × 180cm. A territorial act disguised as decoration. Maximum visual armor: binary contrast, surgical edge control, ballistic execution. No tonal softness, no somatic bleed, no vulnerability. The work commands. Backlit mounting transforms the mural into a luminous spine. Black circles on white glow read as absence made visible: geometry that exists only because light reveals where it isn\'t. Moiré interference at overlap points suggests standing waves frozen mid-vibration. PH3 at its peak: contained geometries breaking their frames, attempting to terraform architecture rather than merely occupy it.','Institutional Commissions',1,1,'2026-01-08 18:04:20','2026-02-12 15:49:59',0,'celestial-secrets-mural-270001','Acrylic Paint and Spray Paint on Wall','2021','A territorial act of maximum visual armor that transforms architecture into a luminous spine of absence made visible.',NULL);
